text: This wonderfully updated 4 Bedroom, 2 Full Bathroom Colonial in one of Millburn's most sought-after neighborhoods, just 2 blocks from Wyoming Elementary combines timeless charm with modern updates offering a flexible layout ideal for today's lifestyle. Enter the light-filled vestibule with built-ins and a bench leading to an open-concept main level. The spacious living room features hardwood floors, a fireplace and ample natural light. The fully renovated kitchen boasts recessed lighting, quartz countertops, a Wolf range, abundant cabinetry and center island with pendant lighting and extra storage. Adjacent, the dining room offers hardwood floors and views of the patioperfect for gatherings. A bright sunroom with built-ins and 3 exposures, a family room with access to the side patio and back deck, and a renovated full bathroom with a frameless glass shower complete the 1st floor. Upstairs, find 3 bedrooms with hardwood floors and a renovated hallway bath with dual vanity and spa-style tub. The 3rd floor features a carpeted loft landing and a 4th bedroom, ideal for guests or office use. The lower level offers a laundry area, and utility/storage room. Outside, enjoy a Trex-like deck, side patio, bonus storage room beneath the home, private backyard and a 1-car detached garage. Close to Millburn and Maplewood shops, NYC trains, highways, and just 1530 minutes to Newark Airport, this home offers the best of comfort and convenience.

text: Timeless charm abounds in this spacious and well maintained home. The curb appeal is undeniable, parks and schools are right down the street, and NY transportation (midtown direct trains) is incredibly convenient. The elegant entrance invites you into the first floor of the home, which offers a formal dining room, updated eat in kitchen with granite countertops, a living room with fireplace, an office/sitting room with built-ins, as well as a powder room and a screened in back porch. The second floor offers four bedrooms and two full baths, including a Jack-and-Jill style, as well as plenty of closet space. The light-filled third floor is a welcoming retreat from the rest of the home, featuring two more bedrooms, tons of storage, and a full bath of its own. The finished basement is where you will find the updated mechanicals and the laundry room. The backyard is spacious, and bursting with flowers and details any gardener would appreciate. Don't miss your chance to own this gem in one of Maplewood's most desirable neighborhoods.

text: An extraordinary modern residence in the Upper Wyoming neighborhood sits high above a quiet street framed by panoramic skyline views.This one-of-a-kind multi-level home offers a rare fusion of bold architectural design, natural beauty, and relaxed luxury.Soaring ceilings, open staircases& walls of glass create a light-filled, airy atmosphere. A dramatic entry sets the tone w/a striking modern chandelier.The spacious living room has a floor-to-ceiling window capturing daylight by day and city lights by night w/an adjoining balcony.The open-concept kitchen showcases custom burled wood-style cabinetry and glass doors opening to a sunny patio. text: Location and charm in the heart of Maplewood! Situated just moments from all the shops and restaurants of Maplewood Village, the Library, the train station, and Memorial Park, this prime location is beyond compare. With so much nearby, you might not even need a car!This charming 3-BR, 2 1/2-BA Center Hall Colonial exudes curb appeal, from its newly painted exterior to its sparkling new Andersen windows. Step inside to discover a spacious and classically designed first floor. A deep Living Room is perfect for gathering or relaxing, while the sunroom offers a quiet retreat or a sunny WFH space. The formal Dining Room connects seamlessly to the large eat-in kitchen, complete with skylight and windows galore, and the nearby powder room. Upstairs, the primary BR suite offers light and space, along with an ensuite bath. Two additional BRs and hall BA provide room for everyone. The unfinished 3rd floor is a blank pallet that offers even more living space in the future. Unfinished basement adds even more versatility, laundry, and storage space. Outdoors, the surprisingly large backyard and idyllic front lawn invite gardening, relaxation, and play, while the detached garage offers additional storage or parking options. And when you're ready for some recreation, just walk down the street to enjoy Memorial Park's playgrounds, garden-like grounds, and sprawling fields for sports and more.Lovingly maintained, 32 S Crescent is ready to welcome its next lucky owners!

text: Discover timeless elegance in this beautifully renovated 1929 Colonial home, offering four finished levels of living space. With 6 bedrooms, 2 full and 2 half baths, and an inviting family room, this home is perfect for entertaining or everyday living. The first level features an entry mudroom, foyer, expansive formal living room with wood-burning fireplace, office/den, spacious dining room the flows to kitchen. The eat-in kitchen features granite counters, modern appliances, and a peninsula breakfast bar. The sun-drenched family room is a large gathering place, with powder room, closets, office nook , and opens to deck and yard. Enjoy the private, fenced backyard with a deck, shed, and detached garage. The fully finished lower level is another family room, exercise area, storage, and half-bathroom. Located in a preferred neighborhood with top-rated schools, NYC transportation, and nearby shopping, this home combines modern updates with classic charm. Don't miss this rare opportunity in the heart of Maplewood!

text: The highly desirable Upper Washington Ave neighborhood is the location of this one-of-a-kind home that will warm your heart. A sweet cottage from the front leads to a surprisingly large, warm, and inviting interior with a living room with fireplace/wood stove, formal dining room, gourmet kitchen, spacious family room, powder room, and light-filled 3-season front porch. Upstairs are 4 bedrooms and 2 baths including a separate master suite that overlooks the lush backyard from its private balcony. The finished basement provides a great play/recreation room, gym, or office. The new owner will enjoy hardwood floors, new windows, and many additional updates that have brought this lovingly cared for century-old home into the modern era. The kitchen boasts warm cherry cabinetry, granite countertops, tile backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. A dining peninsula opens to the family room with sliders to a spacious deck overlooking the amazing park-like backyard of 1/3 acre of fenced, professionally designed and maintained plantings, lovely stone walls, and flower beds that provide exquisite vistas all spring and summer long. Enjoy the property for entertaining, recreation, and privacy, with no adjacent houses on 3 sides. The location is a commuter's dream just steps from the train to NY City, and so close to all schools and the downtown with numerous restaurants, shopping, and the library.

text: CHARMING CENTER HALL COLONIAL IN GLENWOOD SECTION! Move right in to 15 Claremont Drive, a fabulous 3 Bedroom, 2.1 Bath home in one of the most divine and desirable neighborhoods in town. Greeted by bright, welcoming Entry Foyer, the main level boasts opportunities to enjoy a life of ease and entertaining throughout. Formal Living Room with attractive built-in bookcases and marble fireplace; Dining Room with elegant crown and chair rail molding; Eat-In Kitchen with granite countertops/backsplash, custom wood cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances; Powder Room; and beguiling Sunroom with vaulted ceiling, recessed lighting, plus glass slider to bluestone patio the perfect set-up for socializing indoors and outdoors. Second Level offers a lovely Primary Bedroom, bright and spacious with 2 sizable closets (including 1 walk-in) and equipped En-Suite Bathroom. Two more Bedrooms hold court on this Level, with ample closets as well as the sweetest Bonus Room, sunken, with vaulted ceiling and great natural light! Finished Lower Level Recreation Room, with abundant storage space, is carpeted and ready for fun, exercise, home office you name it! Partially fenced-in, level Backyard is especially serene, and perfect for hosting summer gatherings and BBQ's. From NY Direct Train commute to famous Claremont Trick-or-Treating and block parties, this neighborhood is a gem SUPER close to schools and Downtown Millburn, consider yourself lucky to live at 15 Claremont Drive!

text: SET DOWN ROOTS ON COVETED ROSE TERRACE IN THIS IMPECCABLY DESIGNED AND EXPANDED RANCH NESTLED IN HIGHLY DESIRABLE CHATHAM! Premium upgrades, an open floor plan and tremendous space await inside this welcoming 4 Bed/3 Bath home mere blocks from NYC Midtown Direct train, Main Street shops & restaurants & award-winning schools. Gleaming light-colored oak floors draw you into a Living Room with bright bay window, wood-burning fireplace & wall of bookshelves opening to the Dining Room & glistening chandelier flanked by two more windows & double French doors. Behind them lies an impressive expansion with walls of windows & skylights highlighting ample space for a Family Room/Den as well as dining table for the fabulous Eat-in Chef's Kitchen. Custom painted cabinetry contrasts beautifully with honed Onyx countertops & high-end appliances like a built-in Sub-Zero fridge, wine fridge & 6-burner Wolf range. A breakfast bar & center island fulfill the home chef and entertainer's dreams. 2 large bedrooms & an outstanding Full Bath complete the 1st Level. The 2nd Level offers 2 more spacious Bedrooms, each with its own Ensuite Bath! The Primary boasts THREE closets, windows with 3 exposures & Bath featuring double vanity, walk-in shower & jetted tub. A finished Lower Level offers LVP floor in Rec Room, Laundry Room with utilities/storage & access to oversized Attached Garage. If the location & interior weren't enough, the Backyard wows with a half-acre of flat yard!

text: Nestled on a large level lot in the highly sought-after South Mountain section this classic colonial offers both space and comfort. This home includes four generous bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms including a primary en suite for added privacy. The eat-in kitchen is a standout, offering a perfect space for casual meals, while the traditional dining room provides an elegant setting for gatherings and entertaining. The spacious family room features wood-burning fireplace perfect for chilly evenings and movie nights. Additional features include a room on the first floor perfect for a gym or office. Off the kitchen a wooden deck overlooks the private fenced yard, creating a tranquil retreat for relaxation and outdoor activities. Don't miss the opportunity to be perfectly located close to South Mountain Elementary, Downtown Millburn, Taylor Park and the Midtown-Direct train!

text: Welcome to 10 Woodfern Rd, a beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-level home in one of Summit's most sought-after neighborhoods. Thoughtfully designed with sun-filled living spaces, gleaming hardwood floors, and a seamless layout, this home offers both charm and modern convenience.The spacious living room features a classic stone wood-burning fireplace, perfect for cozy evenings, and flows effortlessly into the formal dining room. The updated kitchen is a chef's dream with custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a charming breakfast nook. A classic 3 season sunroom overlooks the expansive backyard, providing a serene space to unwind or entertain. Upstairs, the primary suite boasts generous closet space and an en-suite bath, while two additional bedrooms offer flexibility.The finished lower level provides even more living space, ideal as a family room, home gym, or playroom, with direct access to the two-car garage. The expansive backyard is a private retreat, perfect for outdoor entertaining, playdates, or quiet mornings with coffee in hand.Located just minutes from Beacon Hill Club, Reeves-Reed Arboretum, the NJ Transit train, and Summit's award-winning downtown, this home is the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and prime location.

text: A fabulous opportunity to own a classic single-family home with the added benefit of income-producing rental units, located in the heart of Maplewood Village. This unique property offers a private residence combined with two separate retail units, ideal for owner use or rental income. The property is situated in a highly sought-after area, ensuring both privacy and convenience, with easy access to local shops, restaurants, coffee houses, the South Mountain Reservation and NJ Transit Trains to NYC. The property boasts low taxes, making it an even more attractive investment. While the home is move-in ready, there is also significant potential for updates, allowing you to personalize the space to suit your needs. The two retail units, each approx 650 sq ft, are equipped with half bathrooms and offer excellent opportunities for businesses. Whether you're looking to run your own business or lease them out, these units provide flexible options. The residence itself features four spacious bedrooms, a separate suite with kitchenette. The property's private backyard offers a peaceful outdoor retreat for relaxation, gardening, or entertainment. Additionally, the finished third level of the home provides versatile space that can be used as a home office, additional living area, or bedroom. With endless possibilities, this property is perfect for anyone looking to combine the comfort of home with the potential for income.

text: Nestled on a quiet, tree-lined street in sought after Summit, this stunning 4 bedroom, 2 full bath home offers an exceptional blend of warmth, style, and space. Bathed in natural light, every room feels inviting, from the elegant living room with a cozy fireplace to the expansive family room on the ground level with built ins and a slider to the patio. A thoughtfully designed floor plan unfolds across four finished levels, offering endless versatility, including a dedicated office ideal for working from home. The beautiful kitchen with stainless steel appliances opens seamlessly to the dining room, creating a welcoming space for everyday living and entertaining. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms provide peaceful retreats, and the fourth bedroom enjoys the ground floor. The finished lower level boasts a spacious recreation room perfect for play, fitness, or relaxation and a home office. Set on a rare, level .44-acre lot, the private, sun-drenched backyard is a true oasis beautifully landscaped offering a patio, and ample space for outdoor dining, play, and gardening. A one-car garage completes this exceptional home and is perfectly located just minutes to top-rated schools, vibrant downtown Summit, and NYC trains. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a home that perfectly balances charm, comfort, and convenience in one of Summit's lovely neighborhoods!

text: Commuters Delight - Minutes to Millburn train station, town center, schools. EXCELLENT OPPORTUNITY to move into the sought-after vibrant suburban community of Millburn! Become the proud owner of this centrally located 4-bedroom, 2 full & 2half-bath charming colonial. Amazing location, just minutes to the Millburn train station, Racquets Club, downtown shops & fine area restaurants, CoraHartshorn & Reeves Reeds Arboretums. There are fabulous formal & informal spaces on the 1st level - bright, airy, sun-drenched formal living & dining rooms & the eat-in kitchen is adjacent to the large family room. The newly added separate sun-room could be a gym, office or play-room. A powder room & grade level garage complete the 1st level. The 2nd level has three generously proportioned bedrooms, a hall bath & a primary suite with an ensuite bath & closet. Access to the 3rd level is off the primary bedroom with plenty of room. The lower level has a large recreation room, a powder room, laundry & utility room. An impeccable home with hardwood floors, recessed lights, new HVAC system & a Tessla charger. The large level fenced-in property offers a patio & a koi pond with a waterfall making the area perfect for hosting wonderful parties, sports & games. Nationally ranked, award winning schools & bustling downtown. Convenient location, close to Millburn & Short Hills train stations, fine restaurants, major highways & only15 minutes to Newark Airport.

text: Modern and Stylish Colonial with an AMAZING floor plan. Step in the front door and you will fall in love with the sun-drenched first floor, open and airy with wonderful natural light! Beautiful new Eat-in Kitchen with 8 Ft center island with quartz waterfall edge, stainless steel appliances, and a large apron sink-- overlooking the backyard. Living Room and Dining Room are a harmonious space with a wood-burning fireplace. The 1st floor also has a family room, a stunningly wall-papered Powder Rm and a mudroom. The 2nd floor is a dream come true with a wall-papered hallway replete with a beamed ceiling! Find sanctuary in the hotel-like Primary Bedroom with a WIC, and a gorgeous en suite Bath with an oversize glass frameless shower and double vanity! Three additional Bedrooms, a new hall bath with a tub/shower, and laundry room complete this level. The third floor is an ultra-convenient 5th Bedroom (teen paradise, au pair or guest suite?) that is sure to come in handy with its own new Shower Bath on this level. Lower Level is great additional space for play/recreation and features an additional power room. New HVAC, Roof, Windows--you name it and it's been done! You'll be proud to own this lovely Colonial with wow curb appeal--a new driveway, fresh landscaping and mature trees for shade and privacy. Located on a side street right beside a jitney stop and only .8 mi to Maplewood's NYC Train/Memorial Park this location and this home-- have been worth the wait! Unpack and Enjoy!

text: Welcome to this stunning home located in desirable South Mountain. Enter through the charming vestibule, leading into a spacious living room with a cozy wood-burning fireplace - perfect for both relaxing and entertaining. The eat-in kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and natural wood cabinetry. Step outside onto the deck, accessible from both the kitchen and the den/sitting room (via a sliding door), the ideal spot for outdoor entertaining and enjoying the level backyard. The first floor also includes an elegant dining room and a quiet office, encased in warm sunlight - perfect for working from home or as a private study. Upstairs, the second floor has three generously sized bedrooms and a full bath. The bright primary suite occupies the entire third floor, offering a spacious retreat with a full bath, built-in dresser drawers, ample closets and storage space. The large, finished basement provides more living space, complete with a full bath, laundry room and plenty of closet space for storage. This home offers easy living directly across from Taylor Park - moments from downtown Millburn, close to top-rated Millburn Schools and the Midtown Direct train station for a quick commute to New York City. Added bonus - the amazing sunsets over Taylor Pak at the end of each day, Don't miss your chance to make it yours!

text: Welcome to 82 Oakview Avenue, a sophisticated residence where timeless elegance meets contemporary living. This exquisite home features five generously sized bedrooms and five beautifully appointed bathrooms, creating a perfect blend of luxury and comfort with natural stained wood floors & custom window treatments throughout. The seamless flow from the living room to the dining area enhances the spacious feel, making it ideal for entertaining. The chef's kitchen is a standout feature, with Bosch appliances with a 6-burner gas range & Frigidaire column fridge-freeze, ample counter space, and custom cabinetry that caters to your culinary aspirations. Its thoughtful design ensures practicality and style, making it a joy to cook and entertain in the open-concept great room. The primary suite is a private retreat, offering a tranquil space to unwind, including vaulted ceilings, a spacious layout, a speaker system, custom-designed closet space, and an ensuite bathroom with elegant finishes and spa-like amenities. Each additional bedroom is versatile and inviting, with ample storage and charm, perfect for guests or a home office. Step outside to a lovely deck and landscaped grounds, offering a serene outdoor escape that complements the home's refined interior. This sought-after neighborhood offers the best of both worlds: It is close to Maplewood's beloved downtown village, NYC trains, Springfield Avenue shopping, and just over a mile to the ultra-hip Boyden restaurant row!

text: Welcome to this elegantly appointed home located on an idyllic side street--offering the perfect blend of suburban tranquility and urban convenience close to town/train. The spacious flowing floor plan features 4 generously-sized BR's and 4.5 BA's--this ensures ample room for comfort and privacy for everyone. Step inside and you'll fall in love with the open living areas that are perfect for entertaining and are highlighted by tasteful finishes and timeless design elements like beautiful moldings, high ceilings, hardwood floors and an oversize stone hearth. The heart of the home, the kitchen, is beautifully equipped to meet the needs of a culinary enthusiast with an over 7 Ft Center Island, Stainless Steel appliances, and room for a breakfast table and access to the fenced-in yard. Retreat to the sun-filled Primary Bedroom suite, an oasis of tranquility featuring a closet space/dressing room and an updated en-suite bathroom. Each additional BR is thoughtfully designed, providing a sense of warmth and comfort. The 4th BR, Office/Flex space and 3rd Bath are found on the 3rd Fl. Lower Level is finished and offers great Rec Room Space, Storage Rm and Laundry, and the 4th Bath. The property's well-maintained yard will delight in the springtime with gorgeous flowering trees that add to the serene environment for outdoor enjoyment. This home's fantastic location, a 1/2 mi to the NYC Train/Memorial Park/Maplewood Village, ensures you're never far from the vibrant local amenities.

text: Welcome to your dream home! Stunningly expanded and renovated in 2025, this 5 bedroom, 3 bath residence offers the perfect blend of modern luxury & classic charm. Step inside to find naturally coated red oak floors and bright windows throughout the house, adding warmth & elegance. An open layout designed for entertaining, the upstairs features a spacious living room, a gigantic kitchen adorned w/ custom cabinetry, SS appliances, quartzite countertops, and a tremendous island w/ a built-in breakfast table. The dining room opens to an office/den, leading to a deck, perfect for both working and entertaining. The primary bedroom is a retreat w/ an ensuite bath featuring a double sink vanity and a beautifully tiled shower . 2 more bedrooms, along w/ a hallway bath ensure ample space for everyone. The downstairs includes a spacious family room, 2 bedrooms, a full bath and a laundry, ideal for guests, or creating a space that suits your lifestyle. 2-car garage. Plenty of storage. text: Loaded with curb appeal and situated on a premier street in highly sought-after Chatham Borough this beautifully updated home combines modern amenities with timeless charm. Step into the inviting living room, where a wood-burning fireplace is surrounded by custom built-ins adding character and functionality to the space. A French door leads into the gourmet kitchen with newer KitchenAid stainless steel appliances, and a gas Bosch range. Adjacent to the kitchen, you'll find a well-appointed desk area and powder room. The open layout flows easily into the dining room that leads into the sunny family room with windows overlooking the backyard. On the second floor, the large primary bedroom is a true retreat, boasting high ceilings, a generous walk-in closet, and an ensuite bath with radiant heated floors, dual sinks, and a stall shower. Two additional well-sized bedrooms share a hall bath, complete with a tub/shower. This home also includes a one-car heated garage, with both an interior entrance and a side door leading directly outside. The spacious patio and flat fenced-in backyard provide a perfect setting for entertaining and outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this beautifully updated home your own and experience the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. Plus an ideal location close to the top-rated schools, Midtown Direct trains, and downtown Chatham with an array of specialty shops and dining options.

text: Nestled in a sought-after Summit neighborhood only .3 miles from top-rated Franklin Elementary School, this move-in ready home offers timeless charm and modern finishes. With four bedrooms and three full, one half bathrooms and a flexible, open floorplan, this tastefully appointed home offers sunlit, airy spaces. The white Ultracraft chef's kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz counters, and a breakfast nook with banquette seating overlooking the picturesque backyard also has a roomy peninsula for casual dining. The kitchen opens seamlessly to a spacious dining area with sliding doors to a new bluestone patio and a beautifully landscaped backyard, offering an ideal setting for outdoor fun. Nearby, the living room has gorgeous custom built-ins flanking the gas fireplace. This level also has an entry foyer with custom cabinets, three bedrooms, newer Anderson windows and a recently updated full bathroom and powder room. Upstairs, the primary bedroom provides a private retreat with a primary bath. This level also has an additional unfinished space perfect for expansion - possibly a fifth bedroom or other living space. The lower level, with generous ceiling heights, has a family room, office, laundry, updated full bath and mudroom with convenient access to the oversized two car garage. This home is a rare find, located just minutes from Clearwater Swim Club, vibrant downtown Summit, and New York City transportation (.6 mi from New Prov. Train station). Don't miss the opportunity to make 206 Blackburn Road yours!

text: It's all about the location! This Mediterranean influenced home's coveted Golf Island neighborhood provides tranquility with the easiest access to all of Maplewood's most desirable amenities with no car needed, including Memorial Park, the Village, train station, library, country club and schools. The first floor features an entry foyer, living room with fireplace, family room with stunning original stone fireplace and many windows, mud room with heated floors and powder room. The beautifully renovated open kitchen has a reclaimed wood breakfast bar, stainless appliances and a handy pantry closet. Through the dining room's French doors, a screened porch flows on to a lovely, private yard. Upstairs there are bedrooms and two full baths. The newly constructed primary suite has an incredible en suite bath with radiant heated floor, a spa tub and large walk-in shower plus a windowed walk-in closet with plenty of storage space and built-in shelving to help you stay organized. The attic and unfinished basement are ideal for storage. Hardwood floors and high ceilings throughout. Central air on the 2nd floor. Mini splits on the first floor. New roof installed in 2022.

text: Timeless Charm Meets Modern Comfort! This beautifully maintained 1920s Center Hall Colonial blends old-world character with fresh updates, offering the perfect mix of cozy charm and everyday convenience. Picture yourself hosting Friendsgiving in the inviting dining room, unwinding in the cozy family room for streaming marathons, or enjoying your morning coffee on the deck. Architectural details like arched doorways, built-in shelving with original stained glass doors, a classic mantle and fireplace, and antique doorknobs create an atmosphere full of history and warmth. But don't worry it's not all vintage! Modern upgrades include central A/C, updated stainless steel appliances, and renovated bathrooms. Located on a peaceful, tree-lined street in a friendly Maplewood neighborhood, this home offers a true sense of community - think block parties, friendly waves, and a secret park just across the street. The private backyard and deck make for a perfect retreat, whether you're working from home or just soaking in nature with blue jays and cardinals as your backdrop. With easy access to the Village, the train, and local parks, this is more than a home, it's a lifestyle. Come see why this Maplewood gem is the perfect spot for your next chapter!

text: Discover the fabulous appeal of 666 Prospect St. in Maplewood, a stunning five-bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home in 'College Hill', Maplewood! Step into the foyer and notice the inviting living room, seamlessly connected to a spacious dining room. Enjoy the calm view from the windowed dining room and breakfast nook that overlooks the expansive rear yard. From the foyer on the other side, this home also boasts a generous sized den, a 1st floor laundry room/mud room, an attached 2 car garage, and access to the rear yard. The Fabulous Kitchen renovation (2017) includes Custom Cabinets made by Amish Artisans, Hardwood floors, Bosch Appliances, Sink with Disposal, Granite countertops, Recessed lights, Window Treatments and access to the deck off the kitchen.. The 2nd floor showcases the lovely Primary Suite with Primary Bath that was updated with Custom Cabinet Vanity by Amish Artisans in 2018 includes a Walk-In-Closet plus more storage. 2 Oversized Bedrooms, and a renovated (on par) hall bath with 2 sinks, new fixtures, + a linen closet. The upper level offers 2 bedrooms w large closets and ample Attic storage. The Lower Level Recreation Room has workshop also. Reclaimed Bricks from Brooklyn were used in the 1964 construction. Brand New Roof with Warranty that transfers with ownership. Easily access the New York City Direct train, Maplewood Village, the Springfield Avenue Shopping District, and a variety of parks, libraries, and schools, highways and EWR. Location! Location! Location!

text: Dreaming of a fully updated home in a prime Chatham Boro location with easy walk to town/train--Here It Is! This Stunning Colonial home has been fully gut renovated with addition in 2023. Everything is new including roof, windows, walls --everything! This move-in ready home features a charming fully finished front porch that leads to a spacious Living Room highlighted by a gas fireplace and lots of space for entertaining or quiet reading. The sought after 1st floor Bedroom or Home office with Full Bath awaits. And, be ready to fall in love with the Open Floor plan Gorgeous White Kitchen with massive peninsula island, Dining Room and enormous Family Room space all fully wrapped in windows for plenty of warm sunshine and amazing views of the fully fenced large patio and yard. A 1st floor washer and dryer adds convenience to the list of amenities provided by this well thought out design. The Second Floor features 3 large bedrooms with 2 full bathrooms. The Primary Bedroom is perfection with 2 huge walk in closets and large white finely finished full Bath.. The Lower Level of the home offers a great Play Room/Rec Room with large storage and a great area for a gym and workshop area. Lots of room for fun/games in the backyard and garage ready for a car or-- entertainment! This Dream Home is Ready for its New Owner!

text: Essential elements of this charming Cape Cod home, circa 1956, reflects an abundance of character, style and traditional enhancements. The residence in conducive for entertaining besides accommodating casual living style. The private rear yard offers a blue stone patio and an expanse of recreation areas. Situated near downtown's vibrant shopping and eateries, close to New York transportation and easy access to the developed highway system. Most importantly, Summit has a highly-ranked school system. Community Activities feature The Connection, YMCA, Reeves Reed Arboretum, Summit's Aquatic Center and Playhouse.

text: This beautiful 4 bedroom/2.5 bath split on a lovely piece of flat property, offering a 2-car garage and a wide driveway, is waiting for you to call it Home Sweet Home ! Lovingly maintained, it offers gleaming hardwood floors and crown molding both in the sun-filled living room and in the elegant formal dining room. The cheery 4-season sun room/den off the dining room is the perfect place to relax and has a door to the back patio. The eat-in kitchen showcases high ceilings, a double skylight, plenty of cabinet space and stairs to the ground floor where you can access the oversized garage. This floor also boasts a bedroom/family room with its own closet, a powder room and a door to the back yard. The laundry area is located in the large unfinished basement that offers storage galore! The carpeted 2nd floor (with hardwood under) features 2 nice sized bedrooms with closets, a hallway bath with tub shower, and the primary bedroom with a walk-in closet and a full bath with a shower stall. A spacious 2-door attic accessible from the 2nd floor staircase provides further storage. Entertain on the outside patio, spend time in the fenced-in back yard complete with a fire pit, and appreciate the convenient garden shed. Enjoy all this wonderful house has to offer as well as its superb location - steps to the high school, close to the vibrant downtown and less than 1 mile to the train station.

text: Step into the epitome of Modern Farmhouse elegance in this exquisite colonial home, where character and comfort blend seamlessly in a setting that embodies timeless sophistication. This distinguished property features classic details including wide-plank original floors that tell stories of generations past, sun-drenched rooms with oversized windows, and original doors that swing with the perfect weight of craftsmanship rarely found today. The thoughtfully renovated kitchen invites both serious cooking and casual gatherings, while modern conveniences throughout including first-floor laundry, dedicated mud room, and central a/c ensure everyday living is as comfortable as it is beautiful. Five bedrooms spread across the second flr, including a light-filled primary suite with en-suite bath, plus an additional full bath serving the remaining bedrms. Above, an expansive unfinished third floor awaits your vision- a gym, studio or additional living space. The outdoor spaces elevate backyard living, with an almost half-acre lot offering exceptional privacy. Enclosed by rustic wood fencing and sheltered by mature evergreens, the rear yard features a large paver patio with built-in firepit, perfect for summer evenings. A charming arbor adds architectural interest and frames garden views. The detached garage includes a versatile upper lvl ideal for storage.This is a home where dinner parties linger into the evening and Sunday mornings stretch luxuriously into afternoon. Welcome Home!

text: This quintessential Maplewood Colonial on the highly coveted Courter Avenue is the house you've been waiting for! Large scale rooms and 4 floors of living space, combined with elegant period details, make this home sing! Chestnut-inlaid hardwood floors, built-in window seat, working, gas fireplace and handsome wood moldings add character to the large living room. The adjacent over-sized dining room is spacious enough for holiday meals plus an additional seating area. The eat-in kitchen with vaulted ceiling and breakfast bar has ample storage and is flooded with natural light! Additional first floor highlights include a private Maplewood room - perfect for working from home, and a full bath! Upstairs you'll find four large bedrooms, each freshly painted with hardwood floors and a beautiful, refreshed hall bath. The finished third floor is perfect for guests, work or recreation and also features an abundance of storage space.The charm continues in the finished basement with original stained glass windows and a speakeasy style bar. Complete with a full bathroom, storage closet and laundry room, this lower level is a terrific bonus! Additional features include split unit air conditioning; large, private and flat backyard; and 2 car garage.The location can't be beat - only one short block to Maplecrest Park, nearby commuter Jitney, the shops of Springfield Ave., and just 1 mile to downtown Maplewood.

text: Luxury Meets Timeless Charm in Maplewood, NJ! Welcome to this stunning 5-bedroom, 4.5-bath Tudor home with four finished floors of elegance and modern living. Nestled in one of Maplewood's most desirable neighborhoods, it offers the perfect blend of NYC convenience and suburban tranquility. Inside, sun-drenched spaces, a wood-burning fireplace, surround sound speaker system in the living room ready for connectivity, and an inviting sunroom retreat create an atmosphere of warmth and sophistication. The kitchen boasts quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a spacious island, perfect for entertaining. A formal dining room sets the stage for unforgettable gatherings. Upstairs, the primary suite features a spa-like en-suite bath, while generous guest bedrooms, a balcony overlooking the backyard, a dedicated home office, and private baths ensure comfort. The finished lower level adds a 6th bedroom, recreation space, and laundry room.The deep backyard offers a private escape, while proximity to Maplewood Village, South Orange Downtown, and Midtown Direct trains makes commuting effortless. Additional upgrades include Andersen windows with a lifetime warranty, Nest system for steam heating, a 200 amp electric panel, a new garage roof, and french drains along the perimeter.Your dream home awaits, are you ready to experience it?

text: Welcome to this gorgeous 5-bedroom, 3.5-bath Victorian home, where classic charm meets modern living. From the moment you step inside, you'll be wowed by the high ceilings and tons of natural light that fill every room, making it feel bright and open. The vibe is a perfect mix of old-school elegance and new-school style. Let's talk about the kitchen, it's been totally renovated with sleek, modern finishes, top-tier appliances, and loads of space to cook, hang out, or even host your next dinner party. Whether you're a pro in the kitchen or just love to order takeout, this space is a total game-changer. The 5 spacious bedrooms give you all the room you need, whether you're working from home, relaxing, or having a chill hangout. There are 3 full bathrooms and a half bath, so everyone's got their own space. The primary suite feels like its own little retreat, complete with en-suite bath to unwind after a long day. Central air, French drains and sump, attached garage, newer windows...easy. And the best part? This home is on the corner of a quiet cul-de-sac, offering a peaceful, private setting. Plus, you're less than a mile to downtown Maplewood, so you can hit up local shops, grab a coffee, or catch the train into the city.

text: Updated Cape nestled in the heart of the charming Tall Oaks neighborhood, sits on a quiet, desirable street near parks, schools and less than one mile from the New Providence Train Station. This pristine, four bedroom, three bathroom home with a finished basement offers tremendous versatility of space! Enter the foyer of this cheery, lovingly-maintained home to find a large, sunny living room with wood burning fireplace, attractive dining room, and bright, updated kitchen with newer stainless-steel appliances. A Jack and Hall bedroom with an updated full bath and a second bedroom on the first floor make first floor living a wonderful possibility. Upstairs, you'll find the large, charming primary suite with brick chimney privacy wall, three double closets, and beautifully renovated full bath. Another large bedroom and full bath round out the second floor. With a comfortable recreation / entertainment room and a large laundry room in the finished basement, along with utilities and additional storage areas, this home has endless possibilities. Other attractive features include a fenced in backyard, a huge paver patio, a double length garage with storage, a home security system with central unit smoke/carbon monoxide alarms and a Generac whole house natural gas generator. This continually updated, meticulously cared-for home in New Providence is a true gem.

text: WELCOME HOME TO AN ENTERTAINER'S DREAM WITH MODERN UPGRADES, OPEN FLOOR PLAN AND VIEWS OF CANOE BROOK GOLF COURSE! Enter this 4 Bedroom, 3 Bathroom home through an inviting, bright 2-story Entry Foyer. Embrace the elegant crown molding and shimmering hardwood floors that take you through the entire home. Sunlit Living Room pleases with picture windows and marvelous marble fireplace. Dine in the delightful Dining Room; and afterwards, take it outside via glass slider for an intimate affair or social gathering on the spacious deck. Updated Kitchen showcases sleek marble countertops, crisp white cabinetry, sweet center island, stainless steel appliances, and beautiful bay window. Primary En-Suite Bedroom, and 2 additional Bedrooms that share a Hallway Bath, also hold court on this level all of which charm with at least two closets and natural light. Relax and unwind in the Lower Level Family/Recreation Room, with built-in shelving/cabinetry, red-brick fireplace, and recessed lighting. Appealing 4th En-Suite Bedroom with attractive built-ins and Full Bath is a perfect, private retreat for guests or Home Office. Find Laundry Room and access to the 2-car garage on this level, as well. Magnificent, level and fully fenced-in Backyard is the icing on the cake, and truly ideal for play and pets alike. Prime location, close to downtown Summit, transportation, top-rated schools, shopping, and popular restaurants, don't miss the chance to own this amazingly well-maintained home!

text: Just in time for summer, this fabulous CH Colonial will warm your heart! Situated on a gracious, level, lot with new bluestone patio & deck, complete with areas for great entertaining and play. A quick stroll to Maplewood Village where you'll find the NYC direct trains, charming shops & quaint cafes. Move in today and enjoy the Maplewood lifestyle at its very best!

text: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 4 bedroom, 2.1 bathroom Colonial home in the sought after South Mountain neighborhood. Offering a perfect blend of modern updates and timeless elegance, the home is conveniently located a block away from highly rated South Mountain Elementary School and just blocks to Millburn Midtown Train, downtown, Taylor Park and Millburn's other top-rated schools. The inviting covered front porch and foyer with hardwood floors sets the tone for the home's welcoming ambiance. The living room is bright with hardwood floors, recessed lighting + 3 walls of windows. The adjacent dining room transitions to the newly renovated kitchen (2023) with oak hardwood floors, custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances + pantry. A powder room completes the 1st floor. 2nd floor features primary bedroom with newly refinished hardwood floors, two walls of newer windows and spacious closet. 2 more bedrooms offer similar refinements and a full bathroom with shower-over-tub completes this level. 3rd floor bedroom boasts plush carpeting and built-in storage. Lower level with fully insulated spacious rec room, office area, dedicated laundry closet + full bathroom. The backyard offers 2 levels of lush grassy space framed by evergreen trees and bushes, 2-car garage + the maintenance free trek-like deck extends from the kitchen. A large list of modern upgrades provides comfort and reliability including a new roof (2023).

text: Discover the perfect blend of charm, space, and convenience in this well maintained 3BR/2.5BA Center Hall Colonial. Ideally located with easy access to top-rated schools, restaurants, downtown, direct NYC train access, and parks. The inviting living room features a stunning stone wood-burning fireplace, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance. A sun-drenched sunroom offers versatile space for a home office, playroom, or cozy retreat. A functional mudroom connects to the attached 1-car garage and powder room. The spacious primary suite easily fits a king-size bed and boasts a dual-closet entryway to a private en-suite bath, plus a third closet for extra storage. Two additional well-sized bedrooms are serviced by a hall bath and provide bright, airy spaces suited for any lifestyle. Lower level includes a finished rec room, offering flexible living space for a media room, gym, or play area, and a utility area with laundry. A walk-up attic provides ample storage. Outside, enjoy a beautifully landscaped, fenced-in yard with fruit trees and vibrant flowers. This home is a true gem - don't miss it!

text: Welcome to 42 Parkview Terrace, a stunning brick side-hall Colonial in one of Summit's most sought-after neighborhoods near Memorial Field. This charming four-bedroom home seamlessly blends classic elegance with modern comfort. The sun-drenched first floor boasts an open layout, abundant natural light, hardwood floors, and timeless architectural details. The beautifully updated kitchen features white cabinetry, a large center island, maple countertops, a 36-inch Wolf range, a GE Monogram microwave, a KitchenAid refrigerator, and a Shaw 39-inch farmhouse sink. The kitchen flows effortlessly into the living and dining space, creating a perfect entertaining space complete with built-in speakers for ambiance! A separate family room, tucked-away full bath and garage access complete this level. The second floor offers three spacious bedrooms and a full bath, while the third floor surprises with an additional bedroom or office space. The recently updated lower level adds stylish living space with a recreation room, powder room, laundry, utility room, and storage. A flat, fenced backyard accessed through French doors off the kitchen has a bluestone patio and is ideal for relaxing or entertaining. Just moments from Memorial Field's playgrounds, tennis courts, track, and sports fields, this home is also a short stroll to top-rated Brayton School and minutes from downtown Summit's vibrant shops, dining, and New York City commuter trains. Don't miss this rare opportunity!

text: Welcome to 30 Lewis Ave, a beautifully renovated home nestled on a quiet street in sought after Summit. text: Welcome to 8 Highland Ave., a beautifully updated colonial that blends modern convenience with timeless charm. Nestled in vibrant Maplewood, NJ, this spacious 5 bedroom home offers both classic architectural details and contemporary upgrades. Step inside to find gleaming wood floors, elegant crown moldings, new windows, built-ins, & abundant natural light throughout. The 1st floor boasts a welcoming vestibule with built-in storage, a bright living room with a wood-burning fireplace, a formal dining room, a sunroom, a private office, & a first-floor bedroom. At the heart of the home is the stunning new kitchen, thoughtfully designed with stainless steel appliances, quartzite countertops, a large center island, & French doors leading to the expansive Trex deck perfect for entertaining or relaxing outdoors. Upstairs, you'll find 4 spacious bedrooms & the renovated main bath featuring radiant heated floors and a double vanity. The finished attic offers versatile flex space w/ ample storage. Situated on a deep double lot, this property provides plenty of outdoor space for gardening, play, or quiet retreat. A 2 car garage includes a bonus area, ideal for a Garbar or additional storage. A quintessential tree lined street that has an annual block party, community trick or treating located just moments from restaurants, parks, shops, schools & the community pool. Jitney service to the NYC train is steps away. This home is the perfect balance of historic character with modern living.

text: Deceptively spacious expanded & updated home offering versatile spaces to enjoy inside and out, including a private 14x16' freestanding backyard home studio with heating/cooling, kitchenette and antique wood floors/beams. The main house offers spacious sun-drenched rooms arranged in a flowing/open floorplan across 3 finished levels. The large chef's kitchen features custom cabinetry, island with sink, large capacity fridge, double Miele wall ovens, and ample storage, along with built-in breakfast nook, pantry closet, heated floors and French doors to the deck. Formal dining room plus living room with gas fireplace. A large family room with access to the deck and yard could easily be used as a 2nd home office or playroom. Upstairs, find 4 large bedrooms including the private primary suite with cathedral ceiling with skylight, walk-in closet/dressing room, and en-suite bathroom with soaking tub and heated floors. The lower level recreation room is equipped with a kitchen area, full bar, and full bath and also features a home gym and workshop space. An oversized attached garage, smart thermostats, newer water heater, freshly painted interior/exterior, heated tile floors and more. Situated on a deep lot, enjoy a private, landscaped backyard with deck and large stone patio, fire pit, Amish-built work/bicycle sheds and raised garden beds. Located on a quiet street just 150 yards from the jitney shuttle stop to NYC trains, and within easy distance to parks and the beloved town pool.

text: Move right into this gorgeous, sun-filled 4-bedroom, 2-bath Colonial home on a 0.20-acre lot in Millburn's sought-after Wyoming neighborhood! Nestled on a quiet, tree-lined street and just minutes from Maplewood and Millburn's vibrant downtowns, top-rated Millburn schools, direct trains to NYC, and Newark Airport, this home offers the perfect blend of space, comfort, and unbeatable convenience. Natural light fills the spacious living room, where a wood-burning fireplace and custom built-in bookshelves create a warm and welcoming ambiance. The thoughtfully designed eat-in kitchen, adjacent to the dining room, offers ample counter space and custom sliding pantry cabinets for optimal storage and functionality. A bright enclosed porch provides a peaceful retreat for morning coffee or evening relaxation, while the deep, flat backyard with a brick patio is ideal for entertaining or enjoying the outdoors. Upstairs, all four bedrooms, including the bright Primary suite, feature ample closet space. A well-appointed second bathroom completes the level, while hardwood floors throughout enhance the home's timeless appeal. The lower level provides additional storage in the basement. Beautifully maintained and move-in ready, this exceptional home boasts a newer roof, heating system, water heater, and more. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a true gem in one of New Jersey's most desirable neighborhoods and top school districts!

text: Warm and inviting, this beautifully updated 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath Colonial blends the splendor of yesteryear with all the conveniences of modern living. Drenched in sunlight, each spacious room flows easily to the next, accented by period details & unique architectural features. Step inside to discover the deep side Foyer that opens to the elegant Living Rm w/ a stunning coffered ceiling, a cozy window seat w/ views of the front yard and a WBFP framed by built-in bookcases. Dining Rm w/ box wainscoting and elevated display shelving. A French door opens to the sunny, comfortable Den highlighted by a surround of 6 large windows. Delightful and modern Kitchen with wood Shaker cabinets, granite counters and SS appliances is the heart of this home. Adjacent Mud Rm w/ sliding doors provides convenient access to the rear patio and fully fenced, level yard, creating the ideal venue for outdoor entertaining. First floor Powder Rm. Upstairs is where you will find the Primary Bedroom w/ twin closets and private Office/Sitting Room; 2 additional large Bedrooms & updated Hall Bath. 3rd Floor is home to the good size 4th Bedroom, Full Bath & storage galore. Finished Lower-Level boasts a versatile Recreation room, huge Storage Room, Laundry & Bilko doors to rear yard. Ideally located approx. 1/2 mile to NYC Midtown Direct trains, Parks and Maplewood Village bustling with community activities, specialty dining & shops.

text: Move right into this gorgeously renovated, light and bright 4 bedroom, 2 and a half bath Tudor located in the Upper Wyoming Section with backyard access to South Mountain Reservation. With this home?s East facing and elevated view enjoy beautiful sunrises over the New York City skyline. This home has been renovated while preserving original architectural details that can't be found in new construction homes today. Spectacular grand formal living room with exquisite beamed-ceilings, hard wood floors and fireplace. There are numerous windows for lots of natural light. Stunning eat-in gourmet kitchen with new cabinets and new steel stainless appliances, Jack and Jill bath. Convenient to all major transportation including Midtown Direct, shopping and restaurants. Overall, this Tudor-style home offers a harmonious blend of modern living, natural beauty, and convenient location.

text: Welcome to this stunning Mid-Century Ranch on one of the most sought after streets in Maplewood . This home is bright and inviting offering 3-bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, spacious living room, dining room, kitchen and sunny den overlooking the private backyard. With two levels of living space and endless potential, this home will not disappoint. Situated on a spacious and private .32-acre lot, this home is move-in ready allowing you to settle in, and if you choose, customize to your taste. With large windows that bask the space with natural light, this home offers a warm and airy ambiance. The well-designed layout provides comfortable living and entertaining areas, while the lower level offers additional flexible space to suit your needs. Enjoy the convenience of being just minutes from downtown Maplewood with its charming shops, restaurants, NYC trains and vibrant community life. Plus, nature lovers will appreciate the nearby South Mountain Reservation, perfect for outdoor adventures. Don't miss this opportunity to make this striking home your own. FABULOUS LOCATION, PROPERTY AND HOME. Photos are virtually staged. Owner is a licensed RE Agent.

text: This beautifully updated 4BR+Office home with 5 levels of living blends modern elegance with functional design, offering incredible natural light and an effortless flow. Ideally located just moments from the heart of Maplewood Village, this home is situated on a dream block with easy access to shops, dining, parks, and NYC transportation. The spacious main living areas w picture perfect HWFs boast gorgeous light and a contemporary aesthetic, while the sleek, open, updated kitchen is a chef's delight. Featuring two primary suite options, this home is perfect for flexible living arrangements. You will appreciate the ample closet space in all 4 bedrooms and all the renovated bathrooms. The lower level includes a WFH or perfect private retreat w/ dedicated entrance, and the basement level is the perfect gym or recreation room. Step outside to the flat bluestone patio, ideal for entertaining or relaxing in your peaceful surroundings. This home features a full house water filtration system, electric car charger with adapter, and virtually every surface has been renovated by the current owners. With thoughtful design throughout, amazing natural light, and an unbeatable location, this home offers the perfect balance of style and comfort.

text: Discover timeless elegance in this beautifully updated center hall Colonial, offering four levels of living. From the moment you enter the deep entrance Foyer, you will be drawn to the spacious, sun-drenched rooms & easy flow highlighted by numerous architectural details. Wide archways lead to the tastefully appointed front-to-back Living Rm w/ built-in bookcases & wood-burning fireplace. The classic Family Rm surrounded by walls of windows is a sunny retreat equally well suited for casual entertaining or quiet relaxation. Dining Rm w/ front windows & chair rail connects to the ideally designed Kitchen w/ custom wood cabinetry, granite counters & center island. Delightful corner breakfast area w/ built-in banquette abundant w/ storage plus large pantry completes this ideal gathering space. Convenient rear access to raised deck overlooking the spectacular private yard blooming w/ specimen gardens. Powder Rm. Stately staircase to the lovely Primary Suite w/ private updated Bath & double closet. 2 more large Bedrooms, office & updated hall Bath. Not to be missed 3rd floor is where you will find Bedroom 4 & 5, full Bath & plenty of storage. Finished, walkout Lower Level is comprised of a comfortable & bright Recreation Rm, Laundry & Storage. Centrally located approx .06 miles to both vibrant downtowns of Maplewood and South Orange w/ NYC Midtown Direct train service; Tennis courts, baseball field & playground w/ modern equipment 1 block away. This location can't be beat!

text: Welcome to 25 Sweetbriar Road, a gracious residence nestled in the heart of Summit, NJ. This elegant home, built in 1956 on a .35-acre lot, boasts timeless architectural details including hardwood floors, dentil moldings, and large picture windows that flood the space with natural light. Inside, you'll find four generously sized bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, thoughtfully designed to fit your lifestyle. The main level features a spacious living room with a wood-burning fireplace, a formal dining room, and a large family room adjacent to the eat-in kitchen. A bright corner office offers plenty of light, while a walk-up unfinished third floor and a finished recreation room in the walkout lower level provide ample space for future expansion and entertainment. The two-car attached garage adds convenience. The property is located on a quiet, one-block lane, providing easy access to top-rated schools just steps to Memorial Field, local amenities, shopping, parks, and dining options. This home offers incredible potential to create your dream sanctuary in the coveted Brayton Elementary School district.

text: Welcome to 47 Mountain Ave in Summit, NJ! This charming home offers four bedrooms plus a versatile den and 2.5 bathrooms. The first level invites you in with a welcoming front porch, perfect for morning coffee, and features a spacious layout with a kitchen equipped with stainless steel appliances, a dining room, living room with a custom gas fireplace, family room, and a convenient half bath. The second floor includes three well-sized bedrooms, each with custom storage, a full bathroom, and a den ideal for an office, nursery, or flex space. The top floor boasts a spacious recreation space, with the opportunity to build out a private primary suite with arched ceilings and beautiful exposed beams. The basement with laundry offers extra storage or the potential to be finished for additional living space. The beautifully landscaped front and backyard provide a private oasis with a built-in fire pit, deck shade sail for entertaining, and a fully fenced yard. Completing the home is a two-car garage for added convenience. Additional features include a full-house water softening system and custom blinds throughout. Conveniently located just blocks from downtown Summit, the NYC Midtown Direct Train, and award-winning schools, this home offers both comfort and convenience. Reach out today to schedule your private tour today!

text: Welcome to this beautifully renovated (2023) custom home in the highly desirable Murray Hill section of New Providence. This spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath home is perfect for modern living and entertaining. First floor features a large entry foyer with a powder room, a spacious kitchen, a convenient mud room with access to a deck overlooking a large backyard, elegant dining with a cathedral ceiling, bright & airy family room with sliding doors to the backyard, and upper large living room with lots of natural light. Second level features 4 generously sized bedrooms and 2 full baths (primary bedroom with full bath). The newly refinished hardwood floors flow seamlessly throughout the home, adding to its timeless appeal. Finished basement. 2-car garage. This highly desirable location is just 0.5 miles to the Murray Hill Train Station! Also close to New Providence award winning schools, downtown and shopping. This home is a must see.

text: Nestled in the prestigious Upper Wyoming neighborhood and seamlessly backed by the tranquil expanse of the South Mountain Reservation, this remarkable home offers a rare blend of architectural beauty and modern elegance. Perched gracefully above the street, it offers sweeping valley views for an unparalleled living experience. A sprawling front porch connects indoor and outdoor spaces, creating a warm welcome. Inside, rich patinated Chestnut moldings and gleaming hardwood floors highlight the craftsmanship throughout. The grand foyer leads to a parlor anchored by a working wood-burning fireplace. Just beyond, the spacious living room is bathed in natural light w oversized windows. A new gas fireplace serves as the room's focal point, while French doors lead to the front porch, featuring handcrafted seasonal window or screen doors. The adjacent formal dining room transitions into an inviting eat-in kitchen with custom cabinetry and access to the attached two-car garage. Upstairs, the tranquil primary en-suite boasts a stunning bay window, while four additional bedrooms share a beautifully renovated hall bath. The third floor offers a flexible space for an office, recreation room, or additional suite, complete with a full bath and its own HVAC zone. Adjoining the South Mountain Reservation, the backyard offers coveted privacy with a connection to nature. A perfect blend of classic charm, exceptional views, and modern updates, this home offers a luxurious serene retreat.

text: Welcome to this lovingly updated three Bedroom, two full, one half bath Upper Washington Colonial, nestled on one of the most desirable streets in the borough, where warmth and character shine through. From the moment you step onto the inviting lemonade front porch, you'll feel the charm of this delightful home. Inside, you'll find a spacious living room with built-in shelves and a cozy fireplace. The formal dining room offers a perfect space for gatherings, and the warm, renovated Eat-in kitchen with a sunny breakfast area is ideal for casual meals and entertaining. The first floor also features an office, offering the perfect spot for remote work or study. The office was originally a one car garage and can be converted back if desired. Upstairs, the Primary bedroom boasts a private full bath, providing a restful retreat. Two additional large bedrooms share a beautifully updated hall bath, ensuring plenty of room for family. The lower level features a recreation room, perfect for relaxing, playing, and entertaining. Hardwood floors run throughout the home, adding a timeless charm to each room. Outside, the home sits on a generous 1/3-acre lot, offering plenty of space for outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're sipping lemonade on the front porch or enjoying the fresh air in the backyard, you'll appreciate the peace and privacy this home provides. Just minutes from town, schools, and train to New York City, this home is a commuter's dream. It offers a perfect blend of suburban tranquility and access to everything you need.

text: Urban Brownstone Feel in the heart of Suburban Summit! Stunning Colonial just blocks from Summit's vibrant downtown, schools, NYC transportation. No expense spared in this home's complete gut renovation/like new top to bottom. High-end everything, including an amazing custom walnut kitchen w/Thermador's highest level appliances. Open concept designed for modern living and comfort: Windows, doors, hardware, moldings, HVAC, high ceilings, and exceptional bathrooms for sophisticated living. Must get inside to appreciate. Inviting mahogany front porch opens to a beautiful living room w/gel FP. Dining area entertainment ready open to the ultimate kitchen with high end trim followed by the family room w/wet bar and additional cabinetry, pantry and powder room. On second, 4 rooms suitable for office or bedroom use, plus a beautiful full bathroom fitted with separated laundry facilities. Escape to the third-floor primary suite, dreamy WIC and primary bath, better than NYC's finest getaway hotels. A walk-out LL offers flex space, plumbed for an optional additional full bath, and storage (LL is unheated-walls would need to be insulated w/permits to add heat per the Int'l Energy Code). The perfect sized yard with patio and under deck storage provides the ease of simple maintenance. A home suitable for multiple lifestyles: first home, downsize, townhome alternative...it ticks so many boxes, truly a must see to appreciate!

text: The perfect blend of old-world character and modern updates-featuring gorgeous woodwork, high coffered ceilings, spacious rooms and abundant natural sunlight. The striking new kitchen opens to the magnificent dining room with leaded bookcases & coffered ceilings & offers a terrific open flow concept into the spacious living room, also with a stunning ceiling, and a wonderful den with built-ins. Rounding out the first floor is a new powder room, and lovely screened in porch off the kitchen. The second floors has 3 large sunny bedrooms and a fabulous new hall bathroom. The lower level has a rec room, fantastic new full bathroom, laundry room, storage room plus a bonus room, ideal for guests, and a mudroom on grade level allowing for direct access out to the yard. Once outside, the large level yard offers plenty of space for gatherings, play and so much more. Some of the recent improvements include- New windows, new C/A/C 2025, new boiler 2021, roof 2021, new kitchen, 2 1/2 new bathrooms, refinished floors and freshly painted interior to name a few.

text: Discover architectural distinction in this striking 1914 Prairie School Revival residence on one of Maplewood's prettiest streets. With its characteristic horizontal lines, stucco exterior, and multi-level flat roof, this magnificent home commands attention from the moment you arrive. Inside, the hallmarks of Prairie-style craftsmanship reveal themselves through generously high ceilings, exquisite architectural moldings, and thoughtfully proportioned rooms that balance grandeur with warmth. The seamless marriage of historic character and contemporary convenience creates an exceptional living experience throughout. The heart of this home is the beautifully renovated kitchen featuring custom cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and an inspired layout perfect for both everyday living and sophisticated entertaining. With four generous bedrooms, including a versatile first-floor bedroom ideal for guests, this home offers flexibility for today's dynamic lifestyles. Two comfortably appointed full baths provide comfort and convenience. Year-round comfort is ensured through central a/c on the main level complemented by efficient mini-split systems throughout the upper floor. The property combines irreplaceable craftsmanship with thoughtful updates that respect its architectural legacy while highlighting the ease of modern living. New windows 2025, water heater 2025. Welcome Home!

text: Resting atop an attractive level lot on an especially prime local street, this vintage Colonial home boasts terrific curb appeal that beckons with its charming wrap-around Porches. Richly appointed architectural details like rounded archways, cove/curved ceilings in the delightful Living Room and formal Dining Room, two fireplaces, polished hardwood floors, and the glass-paned built-in shelving in the main floor Home Office highlight its unique features. The updated Kitchen with maple cabinetry, granite countertops, and stainless appliances opens to an expansive, sun-lit Family Room with access thru Patio doors to a large Deck for al-dante dining and entertaining. The extraordinary Master Bedroom enjoys a vaulted ceiling, an adjoining Sitting Room, huge walk-in Closet, and the stunning newly renovated Bathroom en-suite with two skylights. The second floor is completed with three other generous Bedrooms (one with a convenient Powder Room), a Linen Closet, another full Bath with shower-over-tub, and a staircase for easy entry to a fully-floored Attic. The refreshed basement includes a spacious Recreation Room, roomy storage Closet, and a large Laundry area with washer/dryer. The savvy Buyer will appreciate the two car Garage with openers, central air conditioning, private backyard wood fencing, and freshly painted neutral interior + Summit's wonderful downtown shops and restaurants, easy commute to New York City via the mid-town Direct train, and its renowned School system. Happiness awaits!

text: Welcome to this charming four bedroom one full, one half Bath Manor Section colonial on .4 acre, just a few blocks from town and train. First floor features living room with wood burning fireplace, gleaming hard wood floors and french door access to a beautiful deck/brick patio. Updated kitchen has ample storage and prep space and adjoins an elegant dining room. The second floor has four bedrooms including a generously sized Master bedroom. Updates include Hardie Plank siding and new roof 2017, landscaping with sprinkler system, deck and brick patio, Fujitsu energy efficient and eco friendly dual zone heating and cooling system, and recently installed EV charger. The .4 acre yard is a stunning oasis that could accommodate a pool or allow for future expansion of the home.

text: Beautifully renovated 4-bedroom, 3-bath custom Split-level home located in the heart of a vibrant neighborhood just moments from top-rated schools, downtown shopping, public parks, and the library. Nearly one-third of an acre with a spacious, flat yard and brand-new paver patio, perfect for outdoor living.Inside, elegant moldings, wainscoting, rich hardwood floors, and neutral tones flow throughout multi-level living spaces. The open-concept main level features a sun-filled living room and a stunning eat-in kitchen with white cabinetry, veined quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, pantry closet, peninsula seating, and a custom service center with wine fridge.Upstairs, three bedrooms share a beautifully updated hall bath with double vanity and tub/shower. The private third-floor primary suite offers a custom walk-in closet with built-ins, attic storage access, and a sleek en-suite bath with oversized walk-in shower.The ground level features a bright family room with picture window, built-in bookcases, mudroom-style entry with built-in benches and hooks, and direct access to the attached 1-car garage. The finished lower level adds even more living space with a recreation room, laundry area with sink and counter space, and dedicated storage/mechanical areas.Additional highlights: new systems throughout, including multi-zone HVAC and tankless water heater, plus a Tesla EV charger.

text: CLOSE TO THE CENTER OF TOWN, Maplewood Train Station & South Orange Train Station! This beautifully renovated split-level home offers the perfect blend of modern updates & a prime location. The home is completely renovated w/ 4 bedrooms & features 2-zone heating and AC, recessed lighting, custom railings, new roof, new siding, all-new windows, & wood flooring throughout. A spacious 2-car garage adds convenience. The main level includes a large living room that opens to the dining room & stunning kitchen w/quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, & a large peninsula - perfect for entertaining. Upstairs includes a Primary bedroom w/ ensuite, 2 more bedrooms, & a full bathroom w/ a bathtub. The 4th bedroom or home office is on a private third level w/ a full bath on the same level. The walkout lower level features Family Room & Powder Room with access to the garage as well as direct access to the backyard. The finished basement leads you to the rec room & laundry area for added space & functionality. This home is close to public schools, Maplewood Memorial Park, playgrounds, Maplewood library & the local YMCA. Move-in ready & minutes from everything, this home is a must-see!

text: GORGEOUS CENTER HALL COLONIAL ON OVERSIZED CORNER LOT EXQUISITELY MAINTAINED & OUTFITTED FOR MODERN-DAY LIVING! Welcome home to a beautiful 4 Bed/4 Bath colonial nestled on a fenced-in lot in a fabulous New Providence neighborhood mere blocks from downtown shops/restaurants, schools & community pool. Charm abounds in every detail, from the fairy tale cottage front door to arched doorways, oak hardwood floors, multiple bay windows, 2 fireplaces (Living & Family Rooms) & a large paver patio strung with vintage lights providing the perfect warm glow for outdoor entertaining. Indoor entertaining is a cinch with a light-filled addition including a large country Kitchen & Family Room with vaulted ceilings & walls of windows on three sides. Cherry wood custom cabinetry, SS appliances, granite countertops, an island & a peninsula provide excellent flow between the two open rooms. The good life continues on the Lower Level in an amazing Wine Cellar with custom storage, speakers for the soundtrack of your choice, limewashed walls & old-world arched door that makes you feel like you're in Tuscany! A Rec Room & Gym/Bonus Room plus Full Bath & tons of storage complete this level. The highlight of the 2nd Level is the expanded Primary Suite boasting two closets, a Sitting Room & ensuite Bath with double vanity. Three more bedrooms & a Bonus Bedroom/Home Office with ensuite Bath on the 1st Level make this lovely home move-in ready. And it's only two blocks to NYC bus!

text: Discover this elegantly renovated 4-bedroom with three expansive walk-in closets, 2.5-bath home nestled in a wonderful Millburn neighborhood. Completely redesigned interior in 2021, this home is essentially new construction. Boasting all-new electrical, plumbing, HVAC, roofing, flooring, high ceilings, and top-of-the-line appliances. Designed for both elegance and efficiency, the home features radiant heated floors, dual-zone HVAC, and high efficiency insulation offering year-round comfort and energy savings. The sunlit open concept living and dining spaces flow into a chef's kitchen that's as functional as it is beautiful, perfect for entertaining. A standout feature is the two-level garage. Half the space has been converted into a environmental controlled contemporary art studio/office, with the upper level serving as an inspiring loft space ideal for a home office, gym, or media room. This incredible home is located just minutes from Millburn's top-rated schools, renowned downtown, short walk to NJT train station.

text: Welcome to this stunning custom expanded four-bedroom, two and one half-bathroom home, perfectly situated on an impressive deep level lot. Spanning @ 2, 850 square feet with ten spacious rooms, this residence offers both comfort and an abundance of natural light.The large sun-filled primary bedroom addition with a private en suite bath and a generous walk-in closet.Sun-soaked Solarium surrounded by large windows is heated and air-conditioned for year-round enjoyment, whether soaking up the sun or just relaxing with a good book.The dedicated office is ideal for remote work, hobbies or quiet space for homework. Underground sprinklers front & back. Anderson windows except for skylights. This home's thoughtful design and premium features create a perfect blend of luxury and functionality. Summit features a fabulous downtown with shops, restaurants and NJ transit train into NYC. Don't miss your chance to make this remarkable property your new home

text: Truly a pleasant surprise entering into this renovated three bedroom home! Begin with the inviting foyer with powder room and a cozy den with gas fireplace. Just a few steps away, the main level offers super high ceilings, open concept living including the updated kitchen, spacious dining area, and a fantastic living room with vaulted ceiling and gas fireplace. Hardwood floors, recessed lighting, great natural light and views of this home's level backyard with deck and patio, are just some of the many great features. On the second level, enjoy three spacious bedrooms and two updated full bathrooms. A convenient mud/laundry room with herringbone brick flooring and side yard access enters from the two car attached garage. The lower level provides storage and flex living space for an office or play room. Located close to Washington Elementary School and easy access to major highways, New York City transportation and Newark Liberty Int'l Airport. A great house in every way! Chimneys, fireplaces, flues to be conveyed in as is condition.

text: Beautiful 4 bedroom home with great natural light from high ceilings and oversized windows in the ideal Millburn location, walking distance to everything! It's just a 0.3 mile walk to highly rated Wyoming Elementary School, 0.7 miles to the Millburn Train Station with 35 minute train to Penn Station, 0.7 miles to gorgeous South Mountain Reservation with hiking trails, as well as downtown Millburn, 1.0 mile to Millburn Middle School, 1.0 mile to the Papermill Playhouse, 1.0 mile to downtown Maplewood, &1.2 miles to Millburn High School. The stunning living room features a fireplace & oversized windows provide great natural light. The elegant dining room features a chandelier, fireplace & oversized windows. The family room/office also has a fireplace & oversized windows. The huge eat-in kitchen features a large, sunlit eating area, overlooking the totally level park-like property w/ 3-car detached garage. 2nd level features a primary bedroom w/ 2 dressing rooms, each w/ huge closets, a bright full bath, 2 more bedrooms, another bedroom with a full bath and back staircase (currently sealed off) providing access and privacy for potential In-Law or guest suite. 3rd level is unfinished, but with incredibly high ceilings & a windowed cupola at the top providing great natural light. Amenities includes a new roof, new gas hot water heater, new furnace, & 3-car detached garage. It's on .436 acres of totally level property, with a large level backyard! Low Taxes!
