text: PRISTINE BRICK-FRONT COLONIAL on quiet street IN SOUGHT-AFTER Glenwood Section of SHORT HILLS CLOSE TO EVERYTHING! Renovations & updates throughout the sellers ownership, stunning curb appeal w/ meticulous landscaping, make this home a must see! A coveted blend of charm & modern updates. Welcoming Foyer w/ timeless details opens into sunlit living areas w/ fantastic flow for entertaining & everyday life. Gorgeous Eat-In kitchen w/ soapstone counters, white cabinets, Viking/Thermador s/s appliances, marble backsplash, & huge center island w/ seating & storage. Breakfast Area w/ wall of windows, glass door opening to lovely Backyard Patio. Flows into the Family Room for easy entertaining. Spacious Living Room w/ classic wood-burning fireplace flanked by millwork & pair of vintage diamond-pane windows. Mudroom w/ cubbies & Laundry w/ Garage access. Renovated Lower Level w/ built-in wet bar w/ granite countertop, plush carpeting, convenient Powder Bath. 2nd Level features a primary suite w/ 2 large closets & lovely En-Suite w/ large glass-door shower, inset decorative tile, vanity w/ double sinks. 3 additional BRs have renovated closets & an easy-to-share Full Hall Bathroom w/ deep soaker tub & 2 vanities separated by pocket door. Level, fully fenced, private Backyard enveloped by thick trees/hedges. Best-of-both-worlds location in an idyllic neighborhood w/ block parties & trick-or-treating & blocks to NYC midtown direct trains, downtown Millburn, & top-rated schools.

text: This perfectly maintained and updated 4 bedroom and 3 full bath home is sure to impress. Beautiful walkway leads you to the commanding presence of this amazing brick front Central Hall Colonial with stunning architectural details. Large formal living room with built-in bookcases and access to screened in porch overlooking a serene yard. A spacious formal dining room with built-in curios and detail moldings leading into the eat in kitchen with a large planters window and access to side and rear yards. A private spacious first floor bedroom, full bath and large walk in closets complete the first level. On the second level you'll find a luxurious primary bedroom suite with updated bath, two walk-in closets and a private balcony. Two additional bedrooms with walk-in closets, hall bath and access to a large floored attic complete this level. The lower level is sure to delight with a large rec room with natural light, high ceilings, storage closets and new flooring. Plus a storage/utility/laundry room and access to a 2 car garage! Special features of this home include sun drenched rooms, hardwood flooring, central AC, gas forced air heat, slate roof, large floored attic, new lower level flooring, oversized garage and high ceilings. Located in the very sought after Short Hills/Marion Ave neighborhood just blocks to downtown stores, restaurants, PaperMill Playhouse, Library, South Mountain Reservation, NYC direct train and Millburn top rated schools!

text: HISTORIC BEAUTY ON CHATHAM'S CHERISHED FAIRMOUNT AVE. PERFECTLY MARRIES VINTAGE CHARACTER WITH MODERN DESIGN! This stately Georgian Revival red brick center hall colonial embodies timeless architectural charm enhanced by a modern design aesthetic. Every detail from the half-circle portico entrance with fluted columns & slate roof to gorgeous mahogany-inlaid hardwood floors & original octagonal glass door knobs & brass locksets has been lovingly preserved. Inside, the character of each light-drenched room with custom millwork contrasts beautifully with high-end Italian designer light fixtures. Front-to-back Living Room boasts wood-burning fireplace & 2 sets of French doors to light & bright Sunroom/Office. Formal Dining Room features 3 Italian glass pendants & original built-in china cabinet. Gourmet Kitchen shines with quartzite countertops, travertine backsplash, cherry inset cabinetry to the ceiling & SS appliances including gas range. Cozy Sitting Room off Kitchen provides a perfect spot to relax & enjoy coffee & backyard views. Upstairs, Primary Ensuite & 2 Bedrooms boast cedar-lined closets & two fully renovated designer bathrooms draped in marble. 3rd Level offers high ceilings, carpet & 4th bedroom with ample closet/storage space. LL has tons of storage & rec space plus Laundry. Level backyard w/ mature plantings & 2-car detached garage with new roof. Beautiful upgrades & thoughtful design! Ideal location steps to downtown, award-winning schools & NYC train.

text: Welcome to this amazing 5 bedroom, 2 full, 2 1/2 bath Chatham Center Hall Colonial in walking distance to top rated schools and NYC mid town direct service as well as downtown. Guests enter to find large renovated living room featuring custom built ins, wood burning fireplace, custom window treatments and french doors to the sun filled office. Dining room comfortably seats 10, features rich details & opens to renovated kitchen. Kitchen offers granite countertops, fieldstone cabinetry, top line SS appliances & desk area. Spacious family room leads to level backyard with paver patio and private yard. 1st floor also offers laundry hook up, mud room & powder room. The second floor offers a beautiful primary bedroom suite, renovated hall bathroom as well as three additional large bedrooms. The third level includes flexible space that could be the 5th bedroom, an additional office or playroom with storage. Basement offers large recreation room, kitchenette as well as high ceilings and storage. Property has electric dog fence.

text: Quintessential Chatham Colonial in Prime Location! This beautifully updated 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath classic Chatham Boro gem combines timeless curb appeal w/ modern updates, just moments from top-rated schools, vibrant downtown shops, & NYC trains. This beautifully maintained home offers sun-drenched living spaces, hardwood floors, & thoughtful details throughout. A full-width front porch invites you in to relax & enjoy the neighborhood vibe. Inside you are welcomed into a charming foyer & spacious living room anchored by a cozy fireplace & built in bookcases, perfect for gatherings or quiet evenings. The formal dining room, complete w/built in dry bar, flows seamlessly into a bright, updated kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances & ample white cabinetry. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, including a serene primary w/ 3 generous sized closets, & the large updated main bath w/ double sinks & tub shower combo. The fully finished walk out basement provides fantastic bonus spaces including a large family room, full bathroom, laundry area, & a versatile guest room or home office complete w/fireplace. Step outside to the covered back porch & level, fully fenced backyard w/ a patio ideal for outdoor dining, play, or simply unwinding in a private setting. Additional highlights include all new windows on second floor (2023), central air (2020), water heater (2020), detached garage w/ EV wiring, beautifully landscaped grounds and much more! This home is a true Chatham treasure!

text: Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautifully preserved and thoughtfully modernized American Four Square, a true gem combining historic elegance with everyday functionality! Conveniently located blocks from transportation, downtown Summit and more, enjoy the fully fenced-in, professionally landscaped yard, patio with a fire pit, shed, rebuilt one car detached garage, newly paved driveway with high-speed EV charging station, parking for two cars with easy turn around! The interior has all the hallmarks of the style: high ceilings, a central hall layout, hardwood flooring and charming original features throughout. Gracious foyer leading to living room with original mantel, Music room/office and formal dining room. The renovated kitchen is a chef's dream, with top of the line appliances, countertop seating, a six-burner gas range, built-in barista-style coffee maker and more. Newly added mudroom with access to the backyard and a stylish powder room round out the first level. The second level offers three bedrooms including a stunning primary ensuite with spa like bath and walk-in closet with custom built-ins. The third level with fourth bedroom, sitting room, bathroom (plumbed for a shower) and stackable washer/dryer. The finished basement recreation room features custom built-ins, an exercise area, storage, laundry area, powder room and walkout to patio. Dual-zone central air conditioning, hot water radiator heat, three updated electric panels, a whole-house generator. All new Andersen thermal pane windows for perfect New York City skyline views!

text: Welcome to 236 Oakland Road, a gracious 1938 Colonial offering the perfect blend of timeless charm and modern updates in one of Maplewood?s most coveted neighborhoods. Nestled on a beautifully manicured 100x171 corner lot directly across from a park, this 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom home boasts four finished levels and versatile living space ideal for today?s lifestyle.From the moment you step inside, you?ll appreciate the refinished hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and fresh paint throughout. The expansive family room and adjoining mudroomprovide ample space for everyday living, while the renovated eat-in kitchen features custom wood cabinetry, granite counters, and stainless steel appliances?including a new gas range(2023). The first-floor bedroom has been fully renovated (2024), and the finished basement includes a recreation room and home office. The top-floor in-law suite offers flexibility as astudio, office, or guest space.Outdoors, the fenced backyard offers a serene setting with a stone patio, pergola, privacy shrubs, and a playset?perfect for entertaining or relaxing. The detached two-car garage andrecent exterior upgrades add further appeal. Located close to NYC transportation, top-rated schools, shopping, and recreation?this move-in-ready home is a rare opportunity to enjoyspace, style, and location all in one.

text: Timeless center hall Colonial offering 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, and 2 half baths, ideally located in the sought-after Manor section of Chatham Boro.. Experience exceptional suburban living with access to top-rated schools, NJ Transit w/direct trains to NYC, major airports, and premier shopping destinations. The first floor boasts a spacious kitchen with an island, a living room with a wood-burning fireplace, a formal dining room, and a powder room. On the second level there are three bedrooms and two full baths, along with an additional bedroom accessed by a second staircase. The finished lower level features a mudroom, powder room, recreation room, and direct access to the attached garage. A swing set is included with the home. Welcome home!

text: Exceptional Value! Commuter's Dream: 2 minutes to Short Hills Station, 36 Minutes to NYC. Rare opportunity to own a charming, meticulously maintained 3 BR 2.5-bath colonial in one of NJ's most prestigious & sought-after communities. Located on a quiet, tree-lined street in desirable Glenwood this home offers exceptional convenience. Sun-filled main level features a spacious front-to-back LR with a classic wood-burning fireplace, an elegant DR & a cozy den. Kitchen opens to a lovely paver patio & tranquil professionally landscaped property framed by mature trees & flowering perennials. Ideal for indoor-outdoor living, entertaining or quiet relaxation. Recent upgrades include: Whole-house Generac generator 2021(transferable warranty until 2029), Culligan water filtration & softening system. Hot water heater 2021, Roof 2014, interior painted 2025, exterior painted fall 2024, Energy-efficient replacement windows throughout. Hardwood floors, new light fixtures in Foyer, LR, DR & kitchen, recessed lights. Easy expansion potential offers future flexibility. Minutes from the Short Hills train station with direct express service to NYC & close to top ranked Glenwood Elementary & award-winning Millburn schools, this home offers unbeatable convenience. Enjoy the proximity to upscale shopping, gourmet markets, fine area restaurants, Racquet Club, Paper Mill Playhouse, Cora Hartshorn & Reeves-Reed Arboretums. This home truly checks every box: charm, comfort, location & outstanding value.

text: Premier location, generous spaces and historic architectural details make this home truly special. Ideally situated in the heart of Millburn and less than one mile to the vibrant downtown and trains to NYC, with the blue-ribbon Wyoming elementary school just steps away, this colonial features four spacious bedrooms and three and a half baths. From the inviting open front porch, step into a large foyer with a charming gas fireplace and detailed original woodwork. The updated eat-in kitchen with wood cabinets, high end stainless appliances and ample counter space serves as the heart of the home, ideal for hosting and gathering, with a convenient powder room, mudroom and walkout to the backyard. A smooth transition to the formal dining room and spacious light-filled living room. The second level provides more than enough room for all. The primary ensuite includes a separate dressing room, also ideal as an office or exercise space. Three additional spacious bedrooms and a hall bath complete this level. Hardwood floors throughout. An expansive family room with treetop views is located on the third level. The finished lower level includes a bonus room and full bath - perfect as a guest suite. Venture outside to enjoy the deep, level backyard, offering a versatile space for gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying nature. Perfectly positioned near local amenities, enjoy the best of both worlds: a peaceful retreat with urban conveniences just moments away.

text: Nestled just below South Mountain Reservation, this beautifully renovated Upper Wyoming Section home offers the perfect blend of classic charm and modern updates. Located just 0.7 miles from Maplewood Village and the train station, it provides easy access to shopping, dining, and NYC transit plus direct footpath access to hiking trails practically at your doorstep.A stunning renovation means there's nothing to do but move in. The sunken living room features a dramatic brick mantle and gas fireplace, a hallmark of Tudor architecture. The formal dining room includes custom built-ins and a wine/beverage fridge, perfect for entertaining. The updated kitchen, mudroom, and powder room are stylish and functional a perfect 10.The spacious family room opens to the living room, creating great flow and lovely backyard views. Upstairs offers four bedrooms and two baths, including a primary suite with a renovated bath, dressing area with multiple closets, and seasonal NYC skyline views. The third floor features a bright bonus room with skylights and Cat 6 wiring, ideal for working from home.The finished basement includes a full bath, laundry, and rec space and access to the built in 2 car garage. Outside, enjoy a private, fully fenced yard with a patio. 15 Warner blends 1930s architectural beauty with modern convenience near 2, 000+ acres of parkland.

text: Situated in the heart of Chatham Boro, and just a short walk to town, shops, restaurants, highways and NJ Transit, this beautifully renovated and expanded four plus bedroom, three and one half bath colonial home offers modern living at its finest. Fully updated in 2021, the open-concept first floor features quarter-sawn white oak floors, a versatile bedroom/office, and a combined mudroom/laundry room. The gourmet kitchen includes LG stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, custom light gray cabinetry, a dark wood island, and a dual-fuel oven perfect for the avid chef. Upstairs, you'll find three generously sized bedrooms. The primary suite impresses with vaulted ceilings, a luxurious ensuite bath, a walk-in closet, and an additional hall closet. Two secondary bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bath. The fully finished lower level adds even more living space with an additional bedroom, full bath, recreation room, exercise room, and ample storage. Enjoy outdoor living on the spacious composite deck with a shade awning and fenced in yard ideal for summer entertaining. Recent updates include French drain, sump pump and gas fireplace! All this, just moments from everything the charming town of Chatham has to offer.

text: LOCATION! Set back on a wide, quiet street in the coveted College Hill neighborhood, just a short distance to Maplewood Village, Memorial Park and the NYC-direct train, this beautiful home is situated on a rare double lot (10-12 Oberlin on tax record) with everything you need for easy living & entertaining. Inside, contemporary sensibilities abound including a new, custom kitchen offering ample counter & cabinet space, waterfall island, & all new appliances. The 2nd floor features three generous-sized bedrooms and large main bath while the spacious finished attic with soaring ceilings & abundant natural light has been transformed into a full-floor primary with plenty of closet space and room for a sitting area, home office, creative studio or guest space. Ductless Eco-friendly split-system AC throughout keeps things cool and efficient, and modern updates blend perfectly with the home's cozy, welcoming feel. With two full bathrooms plus 1st floor powder room and a finished basement that adds flexible living space, this home truly checks all the boxes. Outside, a lush and spacious backyard is perfect for hammock naps & star-gazing and rivaled only by a heated in-ground pool that is set back in a private setting with plenty of room for summer BBQs & gatherings on the large pool deck. A double lot offers incredible expansion potential possibilities, too! On a block known for its great neighbors & fun block parties, 10-12 Oberlin is the full package you've been waiting for!

text: Nestled in the heart of Millburn's sought-after South Mountain neighborhood, this charming residence epitomizes convenience and comfort. Just steps from downtown Millburn, NYC Train, top-rated schools, and scenic Taylor Park, this location offers unparalleled lifestyle convenience. The home's classic brick and wood facade and lush, curated landscaping create a warm welcome. Inside, the sunlit first floor unfolds with an open floor plan. A window wrapped sunroom, with exposures on three sides, offers a serene, versatile space. The spacious living/family room, accented by a brick-surround wood burning fireplace and timeless architectural details, flows effortlessly into a bright and inviting dining area. Sliding doors off the dining room fill the space with natural light and lead to an expansive deck, for seamless indoor-outdoor living. The renovated kitchen, open to the dining area, boasts a breakfast bar with seating for casual dining. Upstairs, three bright and airy bedrooms await, each with custom closets, complemented by a beautifully renovated hall bath and walk -in-closet. Lower level with generous recreation spaces and a dedicated office. Outside, the beautifully landscaped yard provides a serene retreat, ensuring privacy and tranquility year-round. New Roof, New AC. Exterior all newly sanded/painted. Brimming with charm and modern updates and situated in an exceptional location, this home is a true gem perfect for today's discerning buyer.

text: This is the one you have been waiting for... a classic and modern 6 bedroom home in a terrific location, with direct backyard access to Orchard Park (aka the secret playground) and just a short distance to town. Thoughtfully renovated inside and out, you'll find a bright, airy first floor. The inviting living room anchored by the original fireplace connects seamlessly to the Maplewood room and formal dining space, while high ceilings and oak floors and lots of natural light create a sophisticated and welcoming atmosphere. The gorgeous kitchen has a large center island w/seating, premium s/s appliances, striking backsplash and lighting and convenient access to both the spacious deck and charming screened-in porch perfect for indoor-outdoor entertaining in any season. Upstairs is the luxurious primary suite featuring a generous walk-in closet and newly designed en-suite bath with double vanity and glass enclosed walk in shower. Two additional bedrooms and a renovated hall bathroom complete this level, while the third floor has three more bedrooms and a full bath offering flexibility for guests, home offices, etc. The finished basement has a home gym, laundry and storage and has been water proofed for peace of mind. Efficient ductless A/C units throughout ensure personalized comfort in every room. Outside, enjoy the large and fully fenced backyard. With stunning curb appeal, 6 bedrooms and 3.1 baths, this exceptional home offers space and style in perfect harmony. Welcome Home!

text: Captivating, Classic Colonial in the heart of Chatham Boro. This home exudes charm; an inviting covered entry leads to the gracious foyer. Hardwood floors and an abundance of natural light welcomes you warmly. Spacious center hall - Formal dining room on right adorned with stunning stained glass window; Gracious living room on left anchored by stately fireplace flanked by built-in cabinetry creating a cosy yet refined atmosphere. Upstairs discover 3 spacious bedrooms and walk-up access to sprawling unfinished attic space awaiting your creative vision. Full walk-out basement ready to be finished. Outdoor living boasts a private yard with blue-stone patio accessed by a deck from breakfast room - Plus a large two car garage. Wonderful close to town location. Easy access to Library, shops and Midtown direct train. Top ranked School district

text: Updated three befrooms Home in Quiet Summit Cul-de-Sac! Tucked away in a peaceful cul-de-sac enclave of just three homes built by Menza Builders in 1995, this beautifully updated three bedroom, two full, one half bath Colonial offers the perfect blend of privacy, modern amenities, and convenience. Ideally located just minutes from Jefferson Elementary School, the Summit train station, vibrant downtown, and the Summit Community Pool this home delivers exceptional living inside and out. Enjoy a bright, open layout with a formal living room, dining room, powder room and a stunning eat-in kitchen with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. The family room features a gas fireplace and opens to a deck and patio ideal for entertaining. Upstairs, the spacious primary suite boasts high ceilings, a walk-in closet, and a spa-like bath with soaker tub, oversized shower, and heated towel rack. Two additional bedrooms, a renovated hall bath, and laundry complete the second floor. The finished lower level includes a rec room, office nook, exercise area, and workshop. Other highlights: fenced backyard, covered front porch, 1-car garage with lofted storage, generator outlet, and newer roof (three years). Move-in ready with central air conditioning and forced air heat - this home checks all the boxes!

text: Welcome home to this charming 3BR colonial in the heart of the Manor Section of Chatham! This home offers lush, mature landscaping w/ vibrant colors for all seasons (check the media section, there is actually a list of species, bloom colors and dates!!). The heart of the home is always the kitchen and 100 Van Doren is no different. You will be captivated by the cathedral ceiling, custom window seat and natural light from three sides highlighted by the three large floor to ceiling windows/doors and custom rounded window above. As you enter the front foyer you will be greeted by the gracious living room with wood burning fireplace. Off the LR is a charming sunroom accented with slate floors, large windows and exposed brick. The first floor also has a formal dining room, full bath, office, and inside garage entrance. Upstairs you will be surprised by the room sizes of three spacious bedrooms all with gleaming hardwood floors. The full bath is nicely updated with custom wood cabinets. This high and dry Chatham basement has a laundry, utility room and a large ready to be finished recreation room ! Outside enjoy the patio and your yard as an entertainment extension of your large kitchen. Three magical words in real estate are location, location, location! Your home is 0.65m to Chatham Train Station and downtown restaurants, pastry shops, small businesses, 0.25m to Milton Ave Elementary, 0.4m to Chatham Middle School. Don't miss the July 4th parade on Main St! Welcome home!

text: Welcome to this classic colonial full of warmth and character and located on a peaceful cul-de-sac in Millburn. This sunny 3 br, 2.5 bath home has been lovingly maintained. Newly refinished wood floors, a wood burning fireplace, separate dining room, office and screen porch provide plenty of entertaining and living space on the first floor. The second floor offers a primary bedroom with an en suite bath plus two additional bedrooms and a hall bath.The interior has been freshly painted and highlights the sunny rooms. The lower level has a recreation room and plenty of storage space. The private back yard truly feels like a garden oasis. Conveniently located to take advantage of Millburn's downtown, Midtown direct train and top rated schools.

text: BEAUTIFUL CENTER HALL COLONIAL, FULL OF CHARM, AND NESTLED ON A QUIET STREET IN ONE OF THE BEST NEIGHBORHOODS IN SUMMIT! If home is where the heart is, 19 Hickory's beat is strong. Gorgeous hardwood floors, original millwork & storybook bay window with leaded glass. A charming Living Room beckons you to relax in front of a roaring fire with a beautiful mantle flanked by crisp white built-in cabinets. A door leads to the peaceful screened-in porch, ideal for enjoying a flat backyard. The formal Dining Room brings traditional character with a corner built-in china cabinet, chair rail & moldings. A Kitchen & Breakfast Room is ready for your personal touch the current space offers endless possibilities to make it your own & you have a head start with newer stainless steel appliances like a commercial Electrolux gas range & Bosch dishwasher. A Powder Room & Office with a wall of built-ins complete the First Level. Upstairs, the charm continues with four nice-sized Bedrooms centered around the staircase & bright upstairs hall, featuring an original built-in Linen Closet. The Primary Bedroom is light & bright with windows overlooking the private backyard. The unfinished Lower Level is clean & freshly painted, with storage space, Laundry Room & workbenches. This cherished home is nestled in a simply wonderful neighborhood just blocks from Washington Elementary, Tatlock Field and thriving Downtown Summit. This is an As-Is sale.

text: Incredible location just 1/2 a mile from vibrant downtown Summit trains, shops & restaurants! Move in and enjoy this completely turn-key home sweet home which has been thoughtfully updated from top to bottom with a designer's eye. The wraparound porch is the perfect spot for sitting and sipping while enjoyed the professionally landscaped property which features specimen plantings and mature trees. Inside, find refinished hardwood floors, tall windows and neutral paint palette, and a flowing floorplan of spacious light filled rooms to enjoy including a formal living room with bay window and a large formal dining room. The eat-in-kitchen features new quartz counters, new full height, soft close cabinetry, new tile backsplash, new 36 gas range and new dishwasher, in addition to a 48 built-in Viking/Subzero refrigerator. Room to dine overlooking the backyard, convenient 1st floor laundry with new washer and dryer and a stylish powder room complete this level. Upstairs find bedroom spaces and 2 full baths set across the upper levels, with new carpet on the 3rd floor. Multi-zone central air and solar panels and 2 of the system improvements in place. Outside, the lawn area is partially fenced and you will find a 2 car garage and paver driveway. Tucked on a quiet street, take advantage of top-ranked public schools, convenient access to NYC, local business centers and major hospitals and a lively downtown area with parks, shopping, a variety and dining options and more!

text: Mint condition 4 Bedroom Colonial with a charming front porch, a large deck and totally level backyard, perfect for entertaining, in the ideal Millburn location on a quiet street with sidewalks walking distance to top schools, the train station, hiking at the South Mountain Reservation, as well as downtown Millburn & downtown Maplewood! The large living room is bright, w/ gas fireplace flanked by 2 windows and custom built-in bookcases, & leads to a beautiful dining room w/ chandelier & 3 leaded glass windows overlooking the field, perfect for hosting as well as everyday dinners. The eat-in kitchen, w/ all updated appliances, custom cabinets, & plenty of storage, has great natural light from new thermal sliders that open to the spacious deck & totally level backyard backing up to Slayton Field, which has tennis courts, a baseball field, soccer fields & playground. Seller purchased the home because of this view! There are 4 bedrooms on the 2nd level, including a large Primary Bedroom, 2 beautiful full baths, one newer with a shower over tub. The basement is unfinished, w/ laundry & utilities. Not in the flood zone, never had water! Has central AC. Attached 1-car garage. Low taxes. Just 0.2 miles from Wyoming Elementary School, which was ranked the #1 elementary school in New Jersey for 2025! 1.1 miles to the Millburn Train Station, and even closer to downtown Millburn, and just 0.8 miles to the Maplewood Train Station, and downtown Maplewood.

text: This Colonial gem invites tree-top views, abundant natural light, high ceilings, and modern updates - incl all new windows - throughout. Ideally situated mere steps (.3 mi) to the NYC train and close to Glenwood Elementary and Millburn High Schools, the home offers both convenience and serenity. Enter into the inviting sunroom, where windows span three exposures, bathing the space in sunlight. The gracious formal living room, accented by a brick surround wood-burning fireplace, built-in shelving, and abundant windows, offers a blend of warmth, comfort, and elegance perfect for relaxation or entertaining. A formal dining room gracefully links the living room to the newly renovated modern kitchen, showcasing pristine white custom cabinets, a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining, and a butler's pantry that opens to the backyard perfect for effortless outdoor dining. A newly designed office with custom built-ins offers a tranquil workspace on this level. Upstairs, the second floor features a generous primary bedroom with ensuite bath, along with two additional bedrooms and an updated hall bath. A spacious third-floor suite, complete with a modern full bath, offers flexible living options, whether as a guest retreat or a private primary haven. The LL adds a spacious recreation room featuring rustic beam details and WBFP. Outside, an expansive patio sets the stage for dining under the stars, while the lush, private yard offers space to unwind, garden, or play. Welcome home!

text: Back on market, buyers couldn't perform. Welcome to this exquisite historic home built by the man dubbed the Father of Maplewood - Edward Balch, in 1913. This classic beauty boasts the timeless elegance that defines what Maplewood is all about. It is a standout on a tree-lined street in the desirable Wyoming section of Maplewood, NJ. This home features 5-bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an expansive front porch perfect for play and relaxation, gleaming hardwood floors, original woodwork, inviting living room features a functional wood-burning fireplace with elegant built-ins, plus a Large eat-in kitchen with island, a grand staircase ascending to the third floor. Step outside through sliders to the recently updated back deck overlooking a lush yard. Large formal dining room sets the stage for dining and entertaining. The light-filled family room with adjacent sunroom provides several gathering spaces. Expansive primary bedroom features an ensuite bathroom, with a private sunroom for that essential morning cup of coffee or a private reading room. There is not enough space to rave about all of the features this house has to offer. It must be seen to be appreciated. Enjoy gracious living in one of New Jersey's most sought-after communities.Close proximity to NYC transportation and shopping.

text: Welcome to 53 Madison Avenue, an inviting, updated and well-maintained home offering three spacious bedrooms and one and a half baths in a desirable, walking neighborhood. As you enter, you'll notice ample natural light, a fire-burning fireplace and beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Details such as picture frame moldings add to the elegance of the home. The layout provides a natural flow from room to room, making it enjoyable to live, rest and entertain. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, granite counters, stainless steel appliances and a pantry. With the thoughtful design of the family room, including vaulted ceiling and wall-to-wall windows, you'll want to spend lots of time there relaxing and admiring the serene yard. Step outside to enjoy the flat, spacious back yard with a sizable deck, an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying.Walking distance to schools/playgrounds, downtown, public transportation and highways, this home offers a wonderful blend of comfort, ease and enjoyment. This is the one you've been waiting for!

text: Blending timeless charm with modern luxury, this completely renovated 5-bedroom, 3.2-bathroom home has been meticulously transformed by a trusted local builder, Lefko Brothers, known for high-quality work throughout the area.This home offers all the character of the neighborhood with the ease and comfort of brand-new systems and finishes. The first floor features a thoughtful layout with elegant flow- perfectly connected for everyday living and entertaining. The formal living and dining rooms are complemented by a spacious open kitchen and family room overlooking the backyard. The kitchen is a true centerpiece, offering abundant cabinetry, a large island with seating for four, and premium finishes throughout. A custom-designed mudroom with built-in shelving and cabinetry adds functionality and charm. Upstairs, the second floor hosts three spacious bedrooms including a luxe primary suite with a large walk-in closet and spa-like bathroom featuring a soaking tub, two-person shower, double sinks, and heated floors. The 3rd floor offers two additional bedrooms and a full bath which is ideal for guests, office space, or potential au pair setup. The finished basement is perfect for a rec room, playroom, or media space, and the flat, grassy backyard includes a detached two-car garage and plenty of space to relax or play.Everything has been done: brand-new roof, siding, driveway, plumbing, electrical, and two-zone HVAC. Simply move in and enjoy modern living in a classic setting.

text: Welcome to this beautifully updated home, blending classic charm with modern style! The foyer opens to a bright layout featuring abundant windows, a cozy gas fireplace, and newly refinished hardwood floors. The first bedroom, just off the entry, is filled with natural light from three exposures. The dining area with dry bar flows into a spacious family room with an exposed beam ceiling. The kitchen impresses with Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, custom cabinetry, walk-in pantry, and stylish fixtures. A full bath, mudroom, and French doors to the deck complete the main level. Upstairs are three bedrooms and an updated hall bath. The primary suite features spacious closets and a sleek en suite featuring a double vanity and marble-accented shower. The top-floor loft offers flexible space, while the finished lower level is perfect for a media room, playroom, or workout area. A flat, manicured yard and one-car garage with bonus room and extra storage complete this move-in ready home.

text: Offers due Tuesday 6/10 at 12pm. Come and discover this charming Colonial home in highly desirable New Providence. This lovely home is nestled on a peaceful, pristine street near the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. The first-floor layout features a generous living room with a cozy wood-burning fireplace, a beautiful hearth and mantle, a bright and comfortable dining room, an updated eat-in kitchen, and a convenient half bath. Upstairs, find three oversized bedrooms and two updated full bathrooms, providing ample comfortable living space. The Finished Basement is versatile and perfect for recreation, play, or entertaining guests, and includes abundant storage. Entertain or relax on the over-sized maintenance free deck and gaze out over the gorgeous, level back yard. Manicured and mature landscaping enhances the home's serenity. This home combines timeless charm, modern updates, and many maintenance free features. Very close to schools and NYC transportation. Don't miss this fantastic property and enjoy top schools and all of the great amenities that New Providence has to offer.

text: Set on a prime corner lot in the prestigious Tall Oaks section of New Providence, this classic brick Colonial offers 4-5 bedrooms, 2.1 baths, and undeniable curb appeal. An inviting portico and beautifully landscaped yard create a warm and welcoming first impression. Inside, you'll find wood floors throughout, with well-appointed rooms designed for today's lifestyle. The living room features a wood-burning fireplace and a large bay window that fills the space with natural light. A timeless formal dining room provides a classic setting for gatherings and special occasions. The kitchen includes a center island, newer appliances, and a casual dining area. The adjacent sunlit family room features vaulted ceilings and sliding doors that open to a private patio and landscaped backyard, ideal for relaxing, playing, or entertaining.. A versatile first-floor room serves as a bedroom, office, or library. Upstairs, the spacious primary suite includes a walk-in closet and en-suite bath. Two additional bedrooms, a flexible room ideal as a nursery or office, and a hall bath complete the second level. Additional highlights include a finished basement with rec room, laundry, and storage. The level driveway and garage entry are a welcome convenience. Ample closet space throughout. Located in one of New Providence's most admired neighborhoods with a Summit mailing address and access to top-ranked New Providence schools. Just 0.8 miles to train and bus service. Your new chapter begins here.

text: CHARMING SIDE-HALL COLONIAL IN SOUGHT-AFTER MEMORIAL FIELD NEIGHBORHOOD JUST BLOCKS FROM DOWNTOWN! Welcome to 51 Tulip Street, a thoughtfully updated home that's been lovingly modernized in all the right places. Upon entering, you're greeted by traditional details like hardwood floors, beautiful millwork & original doors with glass knobs. Light streams into the Living Room highlighting a brick fireplace flanked by original cabinetry with gorgeous leaded glass doors. Step into the Dining Room & imagine meals enjoyed in front of a wall of windows framing the private, level and garden like Backyard. Off the Dining Room is a light-filled Office/Potential Bedroom with a newer large Ensuite Bath. The fabulous modernized Eat-in Kitchen is the heart of the home with gleaming high-gloss modern cabinetry, plus a mix of granite, stainless steel countertops, dual sinks with 2 commercial pull-down faucets & gas range in center island. Thoughtfully placed windows allows natural light to flow in from all angles, including 2 skylights. A cozy wood deck sits off the Kitchen. Upstairs offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 full updated bathrooms, including the primary with custom en-suite bath. Third Level is a perfect Office/Bedroom/Rec Room with more skylights & windows shining off crisp white walls. Absolutely perfect location, blocks to top-rated schools, Memorial Field, & vibrant downtown with shops, restaurants & NYC train!

text: Set in the heart of the coveted Golf Island neighborhood, this completely move-in ready home offers exceptional living space to enjoy inside and out, with incredible access to vibrant Maplewood Village, the brand new state-of-the-art library, beautiful Memorial Park & NYC trains! High ceilings, period details, hardwood floors, custom window treatments, a soft, curated paint palette and modern lighting enhances a flexible flowing floorplan of light-filled rooms set across four levels of living space. The modern kitchen features stainless steel appliances, tile backspash, brushed gold hardware & quartz counters with a waterfall-edge breakfast bar. A spacious living room opens to the dining room - ideal for entertaining, and a comfortable 1st floor den makes a great place to relax and unwind. Upstairs, find bright bedrooms, office space and 3 updated full baths set across the upper levels, including the 2nd floor primary bedroom with en-suite bath with double vanity, custom shower + soaking tub. The finished lower level offers flexible leisure space, plus laundry, storage and a bonus half bath. Multizone HVAC, custom built garage with EV charger, smart home features (security & temp) and more. Beautifully situated on a professionally landscaped property with private patio, raised garden beds, cedar playset and storage shed. With quiet tree-lined streets, and no thru traffic, you won't want to miss this opportunity to enjoy the best of one of Maplewood's most desired locations!

text: Welcome Home! This custom home is located on a quiet street in the desirable Manor Section of Chatham Boro. It offers a spacious floor plan, private level yard and the convenience of in town living. The train station to NYC is .7 miles away. The home has 4 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. There are 2 primary suites each with en-suite bathroom. The charming portico with a mahogany door flows into the foyer and large living room with unique floor to ceiling windows and a cozy wood burning fireplace. The kitchen has cherry cabinetry, granite counters and high end stainless steel appliances including a Bertazonni range. There is also a pantry and desk area with seating and a second sink. The kitchen flows to the combined dining area/family room which has beautiful natural light from a wall of windows overlooking the backyard. The yard has natural screening and offers a private park like setting on .29 acres. The basement is partially finished with a rec room with many closets for storage. Buyers can imagine the potential for the large unfinished recreation room with windows and access to the rear yard. The spacious 2 car garage enters the home on the lower level. New roof 2024, New AC 2024, most windows replaced. Chatham Schools are highly rated. This location is close to the elementary and middle school, many parks and fields, downtown restaurants and stores and the NJ Transit train station to NYC. The Newark International Airport is 20 minutes away. This home is a Must See!

text: This wonderfully updated 4 Bedroom, 2 Full Bathroom Colonial in one of Millburn's most sought-after neighborhoods, just 2 blocks from Wyoming Elementary combines timeless charm with modern updates offering a flexible layout ideal for today's lifestyle. Enter the light-filled vestibule with built-ins and a bench leading to an open-concept main level. The spacious living room features hardwood floors, a fireplace and ample natural light. The fully renovated kitchen boasts recessed lighting, quartz countertops, a Wolf range, abundant cabinetry and center island with pendant lighting and extra storage. Adjacent, the dining room offers hardwood floors and views of the patio perfect for gatherings. A bright sunroom with built-ins and 3 exposures, a family room with access to the side patio and back deck, and a renovated full bathroom with a frameless glass shower complete the 1st floor. Upstairs, find 3 bedrooms with hardwood floors and a renovated hallway bath with dual vanity and spa-style tub. The 3rd floor features a carpeted loft landing and a 4th bedroom, ideal for guests or office use. The lower level offers a laundry area, utility/storage room and toilet. Outside, enjoy a Trex-like deck, side patio, bonus storage room beneath the home, private backyard and a 1-car detached garage. Close to Millburn and Maplewood shops, NYC trains, highways, and just 15 30 minutes to Newark Airport, this home offers the best of comfort and convenience.

text: LOCATION, LOCATION, LOCATION! This charming 4 BEDROOM / 2.5 BATH Colonial is a commuter's dream just minutes from the NYC train, major highways, top-rated schools, Memorial Park, library, and a vibrant downtown with shops and acclaimed restaurants. A welcoming front porch opens to a cozy living room and updated eat-in kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, wood cabinetry and subway tile backsplash. The formal dining room is ideal for gatherings, and the sunlit 3-season room with vaulted ceiling offers a peaceful retreat and direct access to the yard. An updated powder room and renovated laundry area complete the main level. The second floor includes three bedrooms and a full hall bath, while the private third-floor primary suite with cathedral ceiling features its own ensuite bath with a stall shower. Recent updates in the last month include: NEW kitchen faucet, 2nd floor bath with NEW vanity, faucet & shower head, and primary bath with NEW sink, faucet & shower head. Other recent renovations include: kitchen & powder room (2019), 3-season room and laundry (2022), and boiler replaced in 2019. Additional features: hardwood floors throughout, large unfinished basement with French drain & sump pump offers ample storage space, 150 AMP electric panel, 2-car garage, driveway for 5 cars, paver patio, and a partially fenced yard provides a great outdoor space. All appliances included. This lovely home offers the perfect blend of charm, comfort, and convenience!

text: Welcome home to this thoughtfully expanded 4BR, 3.1 bath Cape Cod that seamlessly blends timeless mid-century charm with stylish, modern updates. From its striking stone-front chimney and elegant French doors to the beautifully landscaped grounds, this home radiates curb appeal. Inside, the renovated kitchen features a huge center island and opens to the spacious living room with a wood-burning fireplace and large dining area ideal for gatherings and everyday living. A den overlooking the backyard adds extra versatility, while two bedrooms and a full bath on the main level offer flexible space for guests or a home office. A conveniently located first-floor laundry room just off the kitchen adds daily ease. Upstairs, two stunning en suites await. The sun-drenched primary bedroom includes skylights, a spa-like bath with radiant heated floors, a sunken jetted tub for ultimate relaxation, and two enormous walk-in closets with built-ins. The second suite also enjoys a skylight, custom built-ins, and a renovated full bath with an additional skylight.The finished basement offers a large recreation room, wet bar, powder room, and ample storage space. The fully fenced backyard with patio is perfect for entertaining or relaxing in a serene private outdoor setting. A built-in one-car garage adds to the home's convenience.Ideally located less than one mile from Murray Hill Train Station and Salt Brook Elementary, this home truly combines comfort, character, and tasteful updates.

text: Coming Soon Showings begin June 16th. If you are looking for a beautifully renovated home with designer features throughout, in the sought-after Lafayette section just a few blocks to Washington Elementary, Chatham Middle School, Chatham Train Station and downtown, you have found your new home! First floor highlights: Open floor plan, wood floors, plantation shutters, recessed lighting and a designer kitchen with marble countertops, upscale cabinetry, high-end stainless steel appliances, and breakfast bar is the centerpiece of the room, overlooking the living room with wood burning fireplace and marble surround, the dining room and the large family room with loads of windows to admire the thriving, well-manicured landscaping in the rear yard. Second floor highlights: Renovated bath with marble countertop and soaking tub with shower, wood floors, recessed lighting, a large primary bedroom, with plantation shutters, ideal for a king bed and 2 additional rooms easily accommodating full size beds. The totally renovated lower level includes large family, a full bath with the added bonus of a steam shower, a laundry room and easy access to garage. Enjoy outdoor dining and entertaining on the patio complete ambient string lighting for a warm, inviting atmosphere. Some photos may have been enhanced for photography purposes only..

text: Stylish, updated Chatham Charmer. This classic three bedroom, two bath Colonial offers the perfect blend of character and modern updates just steps from top-rated Milton Avenue School and a short walk to downtown Chatham's shops, dining, parks, and the NYC train. Inside, you'll find gleaming hardwood floors throughout, a light-filled living room with a stylish coffered feature wall, and a formal dining room perfect for hosting. The updated kitchen features granite counters, recessed and under-cabinet lighting, a Bosch gas oven and microwave, LG refrigerator, and dishwasher. The oversized 24' x 19' family room is ideal for entertaining year-round, complete with a brick fireplace, skylights, recessed lighting, a built-in dry bar, a full bath, and a direct access to a beautifully landscaped backyard. Additional highlights include a finished basement, first-floor laundry, a storage shed, and a fully fenced yard perfect for play or gardening. A turnkey gem in one of Chatham's most desirable neighborhoods.

text: This light-filled five bedroom, three and one half bath Victorian blends old-world charm with modern amenities, ideally located within short walking distance to Summit train station, shops, restaurants, schools, and Memorial Field. The oversized front porch, with a swing and ample seating, offers views of the local sledding hill in winter and spectacular 4th of July fireworks in Summer. Inside, soaring ceilings, exquisite millwork and wood floors create timeless elegance. Decorative and leaded-glass windows add character throughout. The spacious eat-in kitchen features a Viking stove, pot filler, new soapstone counters, and built-in speakers. The formal dining room includes an antique fireplace mantle and pocket doors, separating it from the adjacent sun-drenched living room. The primary bedroom has an en-suite bath and walk-in closet, with two additional bedrooms, another full bath, and laundry facilities on the second floor. Two more bedrooms and a full bath are on the third floor. The finished basement provides additional space, perfect for a media room or gym. The fully fenced-in spacious backyard was reimagined in 2022 as a private, tranquil oasis including a regrade of the land and the addition of retaining walls with steps, built-in planters, lush arbor vitae, laurel trees, and boxwoods, plus an underground irrigation system. The bluestone patio is an entertainer's dream, ideal for outdoor dining and gatherings. Do not miss this opportunity for an exceptional living experience in a prime location.

text: Stunning renovated custom home on a quiet cul-de-sac, offering 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths. Beautiful curb appeal leads to a sun-filled interior with custom moldings and timeless design throughout. Graceful entrance flanked by living room and formal dining room. The open-concept gourmet kitchen features a large island, farmhouse sink, Wolf stove, double ovens, pot filler, and a butler's pantry with second dishwasher, beverage fridge and extra storage. The kitchen flows into the great room with coffered ceiling, floor to ceiling stone wood burning fireplace, full length windows and a Sonos sound system extending to the kitchen, lower level and patio. French door off kitchen leads to private, level backyard and spacious bluestone patio perfect for entertaining. Formal dining room with tray ceiling, box molding feature wall and three oversized windows. Living room includes pocket doors and oversized windows. Primary with tray ceiling, walk in closet and en-suite bath. Finished lower level with half bath provides space for recreation room, office, exercise room or possible 4th bedroom. Prime location near top rated schools, town, NYC bus and Mid Town Direct train. Unique and exceptional, this home stands apart from the rest!

text: Charming Colonial with Ideal Location and Lifestyle in the Heart of New Providence.Welcome home to this sun-drenched five bedroom, three bath Colonial where timeless charm meets everyday comfort in the heart of New Providence. Just blocks from downtown, top-rated schools, and the NYC train, this home offers a lifestyle filled with warmth, connection, and convenience. Grab coffee at Starbucks, stroll to Prestige Diner, spend weekends at the community pool, or catch the July 4th fireworks right from your backyard. Inside, beautifully flowing spaces include a gracious living room, formal dining room, and a spacious family room with a cozy fireplace that opens to an Eat-In kitchen featuring granite countertops, updated appliances, and sliding doors to a sunny back deck perfect for morning coffee or summer evenings.A first-floor bedroom or home office near full bath is ideal for guests or multi-generational living. Enjoy the ease of direct access to the two-car garage and convenient first-floor laundry. Upstairs, the stunning new primary suite feels like a retreat, with a spa-like bath including soaking tub, oversized shower, double vanity, and a generous walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms share a renovated full hall bath. A finished third-floor bonus room offers space for work, play, or relaxation. The backyard is a peaceful sanctuary with an upper deck, lower patio, vegetable beds, a rose garden near a grapevine-draped pergola. This is more than a home it's a way of life.

text: Timeless charm abounds in this spacious and well maintained home. The curb appeal is undeniable, parks and schools are right down the street, and NY transportation (midtown direct trains) is incredibly convenient. The elegant entrance invites you into the first floor of the home, which offers a formal dining room, updated eat in kitchen with granite countertops, a living room with fireplace, an office/sitting room with built-ins, as well as a powder room and a screened in back porch. The second floor offers four bedrooms and two full baths, including a Jack-and-Jill style, as well as plenty of closet space. The light-filled third floor is a welcoming retreat from the rest of the home, featuring two more bedrooms, tons of storage, and a full bath of its own. The finished basement is where you will find the updated mechanicals and the laundry room. The backyard is spacious, and bursting with flowers and details any gardener would appreciate. Don't miss your chance to own this gem in one of Maplewood's most desirable neighborhoods.

text: This impressive Tudor-styled home features a center hall colonial floor plan. Flanking the spacious and formal entry foyer complete w/ a chandelier is the comfortable living room, and formal dining room. The dramatic 20 foot long eat-in-kitchen with granite countertops, sunny bay window, a built-in desk, and access to pantry and garage space is perfect for today's lifestyle. The first floor also features a powder room, a laundry room, extra shower, and a family room w/ fireplace and access to the back patio and private yard. The second floor offers 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, including a primary bedroom suite with bath and an oversized fitted closet. Additionally, there is a full basement, a side entrance first floor two car garage with built in closets, and a sink. Extra amenities include all hardwood flooring throughout, a full house generator, tons of storage, a sprinkler system and 2 zone heat and central air. Nestled on a quiet street - aptly named Garden Avenue - this Chatham colonial has beautiful gardens, mature trees and artful landscaping. Conveniently located near all schools, town and train.

text: Experience Modern Elegance in the Heart of Maplewood. Welcome to this exquisite new construction luxury residence nestled in one of Maplewood's most sought-after neighborhoods. Boasting 5 spacious bedrooms and 4.5 designer bathrooms, this meticulously crafted home offers the perfect blend of sophistication functionality and upscale living.From the moment you enter you'll be captivated by the rich hardwood floors soaring ceilings and an abundance of natural light that floods every room. The custom chef's kitchen is a culinary masterpiece featuring premium Viking appliances, sleek cabinetry and an expansive island perfect for entertaining.Retreat to the opulent primary suite complete with a spa-inspired bath and a private balcony ideal for morning coffee or quiet evenings.Each bedroom is generously sized with en-suite baths designed for comfort and style.Step outside to discover your personal oasis highlighted by a private pickleball court manicured grounds and serene outdoor living spaces that elevate every gathering.Additional features include:Open-concept layout ideal for entertainingDesigner lighting and high-end finishes throughout including a finished basement.Convenient access to NYC-bound public transportationAttached garage and ample storageThis is more than a home it's a lifestyle. EV connection ready & Smart Home Enabled! Whether you're hosting elegant soirees or enjoying peaceful mornings this property delivers the ultimate in modern luxury and suburban convenience.

text: Tucked into the heart of Maplewood's sought-after Golf Island neighborhood, 26 Salter Place is a beautifully reimagined Colonial that blends timeless charm with modern sophistication. Thoughtfully updated across four finished levels, this home offers an effortless lifestyle just moments from the train, Village, schools, and Memorial Park.The main level features a gracious foyer, sun-drenched living room with wood-burning fireplace, and an open kitchen with stainless appliances, breakfast bar, and direct access to the deck and backyard ideal for indoor-outdoor entertaining. The formal dining room flows seamlessly from the kitchen, while the light-filled Maplewood Room with custom mudroom adds both function and character.Upstairs, find three comfortable bedrooms and a full bath. The third-floor suite offers a private retreat with a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, full updated bath, and a bonus room perfect for a home office or den.The finished lower level includes a recreation room, laundry/storage area, gym, and studio space flexibility for every need. Outside, lush, layered landscaping creates a private oasis, enhanced by an underground sprinkler system, expansive deck, and elegant patio.A rare opportunity to own a turn-key home in one of Maplewood's most cherished locations. Welcome Home.

text: This charming Glenwood residence, set against a backdrop of lush landscaping, offers exceptional living space in a prime location. Its proximity to downtown restaurants, the NYC train and Millburn's highly regarded schools is ideal. Upon entry, you're greeted by a spacious living room, complete with wood-burning fireplace. An adjacent, light-filled office offers a perfect workspace, while the elegant dining room sets the stage for memorable gatherings. The fabulous kitchen boasts granite counters, stainless appliances, a farm sink, pantry & abundant storage, and separate breakfast area. The inviting family room, featuring a modern wood accent wall, provides the perfect setting for relaxation & entertaining. The remodeled powder room adds to the first floor's convenience. Upstairs, discover a luxurious oversized primary suite, complete with a gorgeous new bathroom & expansive walk-in closet. Three add'l bedrooms share an updated hall bath w/ tub. The third floor offers a home office sanctuary. The finished basement expands the living space with a rec room, full bath, wine cellar, laundry, & plenty of storage. Step outside to enjoy leisurely moments on the patio and relish the privacy of the backyard. Detached 2-car garage w/ new roof. Updates include exterior paint, hardscaping & landscaping, garage doors & roof, Pella windows, remodeled primary bath, new basement staircase & railing, and full bath in basement. Chimney, fireplace & flues and wine room humidifier sold as is .

text: Completely gutted and renovated in 2011, this pristine Ranch home features a flowing floor plan from the spacious Entry Foyer, sunken Living Rm with wb stone fireplace & bay window, a formal Dining Rm with custom Pella French doors to the backyard, gourmet eat-in Kitchen with premium wood cabinetry (white), center island w/ seating, Brazilian granite counter, & high-end SS appliances, 3 bedrooms & 2 full marble baths complete the main level. The lower-level features the Family Rm, private Office/Gym, Bonus Rm, walk-in Pantry or possible wine cellar, full marble bath, Laundry Room, utility room, plenty of storage areas & access to an oversized 2-car garage with lots of storage. The backyard features privacy & perennial gardens, perfect for relaxing & entertaining guests. The full renovation incl. all Pella windows, interior doors & hardware, all exterior doors except the mid-century modern front door, insulated premium steel garage doors, HVAC systems, electrical upgrade incl. new service panel, GFIs, recessed lights, oak stairs, handrails & newel with iron balusters, 3 full baths including the Primary Bath with jetted tub & a separate stall shower, HW floors throughout & room to park 3 cars at top of driveway. Other updates include: new hot water heater (2019), Hardscaping, Landscaping, & gutters/downspouts (2020), ext. painted (2021) & addt'l landscaping (2022). Close proximity to the train station, shops & quick drive to Franklin Elementary School. Move right in and enjoy!

text: Architect-Owned Colonial in the most Sought-After Neighborhood. Welcome to this uniquely renovated home nestled in Millburn's most desirable South Mountain neighborhood. The lush English Gardens provide a peaceful and private entrance to this 3-bedroom, 2 full and 2 half bath home which seamlessly blends timeless charm with thoughtful modern updates. Just two blocks to the elementary school, the town, the train and only one block to Taylor Park. Step into a light-filled interior where every detail has been carefully considered. The spacious eat-in kitchen is perfect for gatherings, opening to a dramatic lofted space above, ideal for a home office, playroom, cozy den or can easily be converted to a fourth bedroom. Classic Colonial style meets open concept living with warm, airy spaces designed for modern life. This home is truly one-of-a-kind, offering a rare opportunity to own a distinctive property in a prime location.

text: SUN-FILLED STORYBOOK HOME IN SUMMIT STUNNINGLY RENOVATED WITH LUXURY FINISHES! Jewel box 2 Bedroom poised on hilltop cul-de-sac in coveted Summit. First Floor renovated from studs (2020) by current owner & renowned local architect Tom Baio. Incredible attention to every detail, including floorplan, natural light, finishes. Absolutely stunning curb appeal with cedar shake siding, curving brick walkways, charming cupola and sailor's eye window. Large, open Living Room, Dining Room, Kitchen have 3 sets of glass French doors opening to lush, private no backyard neighbors! tree-dappled property and lovely, European-feel brick Patio. Oversized, all-wood windows at every exposure offer sweeping views. Gorgeous moldings throughout. Full Bath wrapped in Porcelenosa marble (floor, ceiling, shower, custom countertop with 2 custom integrated sinks) with custom wood vanity. Eat-in Kitchen has Bertazzoni stainless steel appliances (5-burner stove) & Cambria quartz countertops. Original 1950s hardwood oak floors refinished. Wood/glass mahogany front doors imported from Africa. Living Room with barrel-vaulted ceiling accented by arched window. Vaulted Entry ceiling lined with molding. Exterior has Cedar Shake Siding from Pacific Northwest. Bluetooth Sonos sound system w/ built-in speakers inside & out. Roof, HVAC, hot water heater, appliances new in 2020. Large Lower Level Recreation Room offers extra space to relax and 2nd Full Bath. Start your next chapter at 10 Harvey Ct!

text: Welcome to this charming and updated Cape Cod in one of New Providence's most desirable neighborhoods. The home features a welcoming front portico, classic patio and lush landscaping.. Inside, the heart of the home is a fully renovated kitchen featuring an eat-in counter that seamlessly opens to a dining area with custom built-ins perfect for entertaining! Enjoy the warmth and comfort of the cozy family room with its open-concept layout, and unwind in the spacious living room complete with a classic wood-burning fireplace. The first floor features two bedrooms, ideal for guests, home office, or one-level living. Upstairs, discover an updated bathroom, a large primary bedroom with both a walk-in closet and an additional closet, plus a fourth bedroom with flexible space. The finished basement offers a large recreation room, storage area, and laundry space, Located close to schools and NJ Transit, this home combines comfort, style, and convenience.

text: Beautiful, traditional center hall colonial set on a quiet tree-lined street with large, spacious rooms throughout the home, a stunning renovated kitchen and a second floor with four large bedrooms, walk-in closets, and two full baths. The first floor has an easy flow between the formal living and dining rooms and gorgeous renovated eat-in kitchen, plus two separate sunrooms and a bonus home office or den room. The kitchen and baths were completely renovated with quality materials and construction including custom cherry cabinetry, high end stainless steel appliances, pot drawers, Shaw's farmhouse sink, pantry area, a newly created full bath on the 1st floor, and custom French doors to the outdoor solid mahogany wood deck. Bright, large, sunny windows along with beautiful HW floors are found in each room of the home. The third floor has a bright walk-up staircase and two rooms ready to be created into a fifth bedroom and bathroom with existing plumbing. Basement features high ceilings with laundry area, utility room, workshop, storage room, and potential to finish into a large rec room space. The 2-car garage, completely renovated, can easily fit two SUV size cars and has loft storage. Large, flat, level lot with fenced in backyard, and perennial gardens. One of the largest lots on this block of Rutgers St. Less than 1 mile to Maplewood train station and downtown village.

text: Welcome to 165 Passaic Ave A Brand-New Construction Home Built in 2025 ! This stunning modern residence offers the perfect blend of thoughtful design, high-end finishes, and future-ready features. With 5 spacious bedrooms (including 1 on the fully finished lower level) and 3.5 luxurious bathrooms, this home provides ample space for comfort and functionality. Designed with everyday living and entertaining in mind, the home features an open floor plan with a double sliding door that opens to a beautifully landscaped backyard with already built in grill and outdoor kitchen - creating seamless indoor-outdoor flow and the perfect setting for gatherings or quiet relaxation. Additional highlights include: Smart thermostats for energy-efficient climate control, EV charger for eco-conscious convenience, Chef's kitchen with premium appliances and sleek finishes; Washer/Dryer Combo. Attached garage and modern exterior with great curb appeal. Set in a desirable location, this turnkey home delivers sophisticated living with all the benefits of brand-new construction, just unpack and enjoy.

text: FULLY RENOVATED, PICTURE PERFECT 4 BEDROOM, 2.2 BATH COLONIAL PREMIER LOCATION JUST A QUICK WALK TO MAPLEWOOD VILLAGE & THE TRAIN TO NYC. Welcome to 90 Oakview Avenue, a chic & stylish 4 bedroom, 2.2 bath Colonial in an amazing walk to town & train location. Step through the unique glass vestibule & enjoy the open concept first level with rich hardwood floors, high ceilings, elegant living room with fireplace, gracious dining room & charming sunroom/playroom. The renovated kitchen features a breakfast bar, quartz counters, subway tile backsplash & stainless steel appliances. Off the kitchen is a powder room & mudroom with backyard access. The second level offers plenty of space with 3 bedrooms, a full bath & sunny reading nook. The standout primary suite occupies the third level & features a renovated bath, huge closets & extra space for a home office setup. The finished lower level is the perfect spot for indoor play with a large rec room, laundry room, half bath & plenty of storage. Step outside & prepare to be wowed by the gorgeous property with open lawns, deck, new patio with space for dining & relaxing & 2-car garage. Added bonuses include 2-zone central air & a french drain with sump pumps for peace of mind. 90 Oakview perfectly blends timeless elegance with thoughtful upgrades & is located in a prime Maplewood neighborhood just steps to town. Everything has been done, just unpack your bags and move right in!

text: Welcome to 46 Locust Drive, a charming three bedroom, two full, one half bath Colonial just 0.6 miles from Summit's vibrant downtown and NJ Transit station. This classic home offers the perfect blend of convenience, charm, and comfort. The first floor is open and airy, with an abundance of natural light and newer hardwood floors and features an eat-in kitchen, a formal dining room, a sunlit living room, a private office, an oversized foyer, and a convenient powder room. Upstairs, you'll find three comfortable bedrooms, including an expansive primary bedroom along with a full bath with tub and shower. The inviting finished basement with high ceilings, beautiful wood floors and multiple windows is perfect for a recreation room, home gym, or office. Outside, enjoy the level 0.23-acre lot and rare oversized three car detached garage ideal for extra storage, hobbies, or car enthusiasts. Located in one of Summit's most convenient neighborhoods, this home is only .5 miles to Brayton School and Memorial Field, .6 miles to Summit Middle School and .7 miles to Summit High School. With its unbeatable location, functional layout, and thoughtful updates, 46 Locust Drive offers the perfect blend of convenience, character, and comfort.

text: An extraordinary modern residence in the Upper Wyoming neighborhood sits high above a quiet street framed by panoramic skyline views.This one-of-a-kind multi-level home offers a rare fusion of bold architectural design, natural beauty, and relaxed luxury.Soaring ceilings, open staircases& walls of glass create a light-filled, airy atmosphere. A dramatic entry sets the tone w/a striking modern chandelier.The spacious living room has a floor-to-ceiling window capturing daylight by day and city lights by night w/an adjoining balcony.The open-concept kitchen showcases custom burled wood-style cabinetry and glass doors opening to a sunny patio. A formal dining room with a built-in glass cabinet opens to a second balcony.The family room features a wood-burning fireplace&leads to a deck overlooking a koi pond and waterfall.A bright sunroom with Pella doors leads to a string-lit deck perfect for entertaining.This level includes an office/bedroom, half bath, laundry and gym with private shower.Oversized garage&storage are below.Upstairs the serene primary suite offers a spa-like bath with Oceania tub, radiant floors, glass shower, dual sinks, Toto washlet, and Moon Tile porcelain.An En-suite guest room shares the level.Steps up, two more bedrooms with lofts share hall bath.The pinnacle is a theater with plush carpet, office nook& NYC skyline views.Every detail of this home is crafted for comfort, creativity and connection AND just minutes from Midtown Direct trains, Jitney & vibrant downtown!

text: Tucked away on a quiet cul-de-sac in Summit's desirable Woodland Park neighborhood, this turnkey Colonial offers modern comfort, timeless style, and a prime location. Fully renovated in 2018, the home features four bedrooms, two full, one half baths, and a bright, open layout designed for everyday living and entertaining.The first floor flows effortlessly between living, dining, and kitchen spaces, while the upstairs offers four generously sized bedrooms including a serene primary suite. Downstairs, a finished lower level provides flexible space for a playroom, gym, or home office.Step outside to enjoy the newly landscaped front and back yards, complete with a full irrigation system and invisible dog fence, perfect for both entertaining and everyday play.Extras include a mudroom with cubbies and washer/dryer. Located within the top-rated Franklin School district and just minutes from downtown Summit, this home checks every box.

text: Conveniently situated in close proximity to town, schools and NYC train, this wonderful 3-step ranch is the epitome of carefree living. This home has been thoughtfully updated throughout and provides a comfortable backdrop for entertaining and everyday living. The heart of the home is a warm and functional chef's kitchen with high-end stainless appliances, including a Blue Star oven/range, Bosch refrigerator & dishwasher, and Jenn-air microwave, cherry cabinets, quartz countertops, a modern tile backsplash and copious counter space & storage. The kitchen is open to a large dining room and in close proximity to a generously sized living room with wood-burning fireplace. An adjacent playroom/office overlooks the tranquil backyard. Just a few steps up, you will find 3 bedrooms, including a master suite with large custom closets and a renovated en-suite bath. A second renovated full bath with tub rounds out this level. The unfinished basement is full of possibilities. With high ceilings and tons of storage, buyers can easily make this space their own. An attached oversized 2 car garage is an additional bonus. The fully fenced backyard is a private oasis, with a large stone patio, mature trees and play set included. Renovations include updated kitchen and baths, hardwood floors, windows and exterior doors, HVAC, HWH, backyard fence, front & back hardscaping, garage doors and closet organization systems. Fireplace, chimneys and flues sold as-is .

text: Nestled on a tranquil, tree-lined street and ideally situated mere moments from the vibrant heart of downtown Maplewood, this beautifully renovated 5-bedroom, 2.2-bathroom colonial home presents a rare opportunity. It is a true gem, masterfully blending timeless architectural charm with an array of modern upgrades and elegant finishes.Step inside and discover a residence that offers the perfect balance for today's living. The thoughtfully designed layout provides both spacious entertaining areas and intimate retreats. The large living room with built-ins, fireplace & window seat is the perfect welcome leading to the formal dining room. The kitchen flows from the dining room and features Stainless Steel appliances and granite countertops. The light filled family room rounds out the spacious first floor. Upstairs the home has 5 large bedrooms and two full baths. The private master suite has the sought after walk in closet/dressing room & primary bathroom The finished lower level had not one but two recreation/bonus rooms plus a powder room, laundry and storage. Beyond the interiors, this property extends its appeal. The large back yard (lot size 50x136) offers additional space for relaxation and enjoyment and an inviting patio, perfect for al fresco dining and entertaining.1 Winthrop Place is equipped with solar panels - a significant enhancement that enables future homeowners the opportunity to lessen their PSEG bills and enjoy more sustainable living.

text: CHARMING MAPLEWOOD 5-BED COLONIAL OFFERS VACATION-LIKE RETREAT CLOSE TO EVERYTHING! Welcome home to 108 Wyoming Ave, ideally located just minutes from Maplewood Village & South Orange, both with NYC trains, shops, restaurants & vibrant events. The stone & stucco house features leaded glass windows, original molding & millwork, 2 wood-burning fireplaces & beautiful white oak hardwood floors throughout. Kitchen boasts custom inset cabinetry in slate blue, soapstone countertops & integrated sink, white subway tile, SS appliances inc. 6-burner gas cooktop & double wall ovens, & center island. Breakfast nook offers a wall of cabinets & access to a large maintenance-free deck. Front-to-back Living Room has arched bookcases flanking the door to an inviting Sunroom with walls of windows & access to the back deck. Spacious formal Dining Room & Powder Room round out this level. Second Level features 4 good-sized bedrooms, 2 well-appointed full baths & tons of space in the California Closets throughout. Third Level offers another full Bath, Bedroom & more great storage space inc. fully lined cedar closet. The real vacation experience is found on the Lower Level with a large second sunroom with windows on 3 exposures with optional screens, built-in hot tub, & access to a Family Room with a stone fireplace! A Full Bath, Laundry and 2-car Garage access complete the picture. Fully fenced-in backyard, proximity to schools, transit & shopping. Don't miss this Maplewood charmer!

text: FULLY RENOVATED COLONIAL W/ BEAUTIFUL GARDENS STEPS FROM THE NEW PROV TRAIN STATION! Corner lot in one of the most desirable neighborhoods in town sits a modern-day masterpiece of design. With every detail thoughtfully crafted, this cedar-clad home brings together the perfect mix of contemporary style & warmth. Outside a gardener's paradise awaits, ripe with perennial gardens, fruit trees, winding walkways, and a grapevine arbor. Open floor plan, crisp white walls, incredible natural light & wide-plank white oak floors bring a sense of peace & calm to all who grace this home. Spacious & bright Living Room invites entry from the Front Porch, both w/ steel accents. The open Dining Room & expansive Chef's Kitchen continue to impress w/ custom cabinetry, windows with three exposures, modern brass sputnik chandelier, massive island with prep sink, SS appliances including 48-in. gas Z-line convection range & Bosch dishwasher, plus room for a wine fridge under the custom-designed wood & steel staircase. Family Room sits besides the gorgeous kitchen w/ views of the winding creek through French doors. Full Bathroom rounds out the 1st Level. 3 spacious Bedrooms, including a Primary Ensuite are the highlight of the 2nd Level w/ a Laundry Closet & additional Full Bath. Bright 3rd Level is the perfect Studio, bonus Bedroom or Rec Room w/ windows & half Bath. The real showpiece is the garden with flowering perennials, fruit trees, raised beds & grapevine arbor. Don't miss this!
